order-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:18px"><span style="color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><br/></span></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:18px"><span style="color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"></span></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">加入了梦校计划后，我遇到了经验丰富、让我受益颇多的专业导师。自己一开始只知道要申请流行病学，但了解尚浅。和专业导师沟通下来发现，她对这方面的信息掌握的很多，对各个学校的项目也都了如指掌，比如：某个学校的项目是偏实际还是理论。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">她从多维度出发，以内行人的身份给了我很多重要的 insights</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">之后，基于专业导师的分享，我也会自己去网上查询一些信息。查询后发现，很多信息导师早已经详细地跟我说过，我就觉得：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">有相关经历的人陪伴我一起申请，是一件很靠谱的事情。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size:18px"><span style="color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><br/></span></span></strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167,