    </section>            </section>        </section>    </section></section><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <br/></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <strong style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size:18px"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong>心系科研，一路成长</strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong></strong></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">当初高考选择专业的时候，我就有未来走学术做研究的想法，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">再加上对新材料有点兴趣，所以选择了这个专业。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我们学校有个特色：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">本科的时候是导师制。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">这样一来，所有想去实验室的同学都有机会，并且</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">可以自由选择课题组、研究方向和专业导师。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">因为我进大学时就有走学术的想法，所以我比其他同学早一步进入实验室，跟着师兄师姐做课题，他们也会启发我去思考一些感兴趣的问题，这也让我对科研工作有了一定概念，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">让我更加坚定地走科研这条路。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea65c048f8b796a9621bcfa" style="width: 410px; height: 245px;"/></strong></span></span><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong></strong></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">本科阶段，我做的研究主要集中于电极材料，曾和导师以及学长学姐一起集中探讨研究纳米材料在储能方向的应用。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">最难的地方是合成材料，我们当时在这里卡壳了很久，最后通过对材料纳米化将其颗粒变得更小来提高其储能性能。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">当成果得以论文的形式成功发表的时候，自己的内心也充满成就感。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">因为有了相关知识基础以及科研实践，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">所以我在申请的时候着重考查了与电极材料研究相关的学校，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">例如佐治亚理工、密歇根安娜堡分校等。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">再加上</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我一直对计算机在材料方面的应用非常感兴趣，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">虽然本科阶段接触得不多，但我觉得这应该是材料科学专业未来发展的一大趋势，所以材料科学和计算机专业实力都非常强劲的 CMU 成了我申请的冲刺校。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <br/></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong>因为语言，被动 Gap</strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong></strong></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">这部分就是我的“教训展示”了——语言刷分是我最痛苦的事情，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我前后考了 6 次托福和 4 次 GRE&nbsp;，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">真的是给 ETS “送了不少钱”。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">没有满意的语言成绩，也成为</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我 Gap 一年的主要原因。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <br/></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea65c528f8b796a9621bd12"/></strong></span></span><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong></strong></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">回想这段辛酸刷分路，造成这种结果的原因有两点：</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"></span></p><section>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;">                            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">reason 1 ：</span>                        </p>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section></section><p></p><section>    <section>        <section>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">刚开始的观念有很大的误区：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">认为托</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">福考试，突击就会有成效，所以一味注重技巧，没打好基础，时间也没有付出够。</span>            </p>        </section>    </section></section><p></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <br/></p><section>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;">                            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">reason 2 ：</span>                        </p>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </sec