b(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>            </p><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal;">在 Gap 这一年里，我把大部分的精力投入到语言考试的准备上，每天给自己制定量化目标，无论多晚都要当天完成。</span>        </section>    </section></section><p></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea65c978f8b796a9621bd18" style="width: 426px; height: 297px;"/></strong></span></span><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong></strong></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">为了提高自己的口语成绩，自己反思前几次考试失利的原因，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">认为自己口语备考的态度和方法存在问题：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">心态上有点抵触，每次都把口语练习拖到最后；</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">复习也只是单纯地背语料，没有真正达到 speak 的状态。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">为了逼迫自己张口说英语，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我在&nbsp;app&nbsp;上、网站上搜寻了很多&nbsp;partners&nbsp;，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">终于找到了一位目标很一致的 partner ，一起练口语。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">事实证明，给自己营造一个语言环境很重要，和 partner 练习近三周，我自己开口说英语的感觉和以前有了很大变化，不再是被动地输出，而是能迅速组织自己的思路有条理地表达出来。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">最后到 11 月初的时候，真的已经到悬崖边上了，托福终于刷出了 105 分的成绩。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea65cc78f8b796a9621bd20" style="width: 443px; height: 266px;"/></strong></span></span><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong></strong></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">语</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">言成绩获得质变，从我个人经历和感受看来，其实需要前期大量的训练和积累作为基础。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">大家常说“得听力者得托福”，而我前几次考试听力都只在 20 分左右徘徊，后期备考的时候我几乎将一半的时间用在了“磨耳朵”上，精听、泛听、跟读......听到一定量了真的会有感觉。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我觉得在最后一次考试前，我应该是做到了这个量，所以听力赢来质变，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">一下子考到了 29 分。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/>结缘棕榈，保驾护航</strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong></strong></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">因为我语言成绩一直刷不出来，再加上自己又有点“拖延症”，所以</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我觉得非常有必要找个专业的团队来帮助我。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">在网上搜索机构的时候，棕榈超高的好评度吸引了我，和棕榈前期咨询的老师沟通了解之后，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">觉得棕榈给人感觉非常积极向上，所以决定和棕榈牵手。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">现在看来，这确实是个很棒的决定。</span><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">棕榈给我的帮助</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">首先在于选校上，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我的选校列表改过多次，到最后终于刷出语言成绩后才定下来。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">这期间，我的主导师和专业导师都给予了我非常详细的选校建议，将学校优势一一给我讲述清楚。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">之前说过，我对计算机在材料方面的研究比较感兴趣，CMU 是我选择的冲刺校之一，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">棕榈给我匹配的专业导师刚好也是 CMU 该专业的学长，他给了我许多选校的建议，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">让我对美国学校有了更加清晰的认识，包括未来如何规划研究生生活。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea65d238f8b796a9621bd2d" style="width: 454px; height: 240px;"/></strong></span></span><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong></strong></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">其次在文书写作上，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我的初稿其实有不少问题，逻辑不太清晰，故事比较琐碎。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我的主导师帮我厘清和筛选主要事件后，让我顿时有了改进的方向。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">因为我的核心部分是介绍我的科研经历，我的主导师也建议我将这部分讲述得更加具体，例如提及一些核心数据，运用的方法，以及重要步骤的结果等等。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">这些细节的加入体现了我的科研能力以及课题价值，这些点更契合招生官审核的要求</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">最后一点，也是非常重要的一点。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">导师们给予我的鼓励和陪伴真的很贴心，让我感到非常温暖。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">因为我有点喜欢拖延，所以常常把事情拖到晚上，又有些事情自己不会解决，需要在群里寻求导师帮助。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">记得有次已经是晚上 11 点多了，我的导师们都几乎是秒回我消息，问题得到非常及时的解决。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea65d5e8f8b796a9621bd35" style="width: 400px; height: 385px;"/></strong></span></span><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="color:#28a7a9;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, Helvetica Neue, PingFang SC, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft YaHei UI, Microsoft YaHei, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:18px"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong></strong></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: rgb