low-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">像 edX 和 Coursera，还有学堂在线都有很多网课；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">另一个是去上暑校，</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我当时有 2 个暑期学校的 offer 可供选择，一个是日内瓦国际关系及发展高等学院的一个暑期项目，还有一个是 KCL 的暑期项目，但是我后来还是选择了 KCL，主要还是因为它的国关的专业程度比较高，课程设置比较系统化，而日内瓦的暑校主要偏人文、哲学类的补充学习，侧重实习一点。最后我觉得专业知识的学习比较重要，棕榈的导师也这样建议，就选了 KCL 的课。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-decoration-line: underline; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">第二个是研究经历的补充。</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">文科类其实比较难去找研究项目，为了补充研究经历，在</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">校内课程论文、科研类竞赛活动、毕业设计的课题上，我都特意选择了跟国际关系相关的方面。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">这些都是在确定了转专业之后的有目的的调整。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-decoration-line: underline; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-wo