 GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <br/></p><p style="text-align: left; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">比方说面试的时候，除了硬性内容的准备，和面试官的联系与交谈应该用什么样的态度、称呼和措辞？</em><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">这些我拿不准都会去问导师</em><em style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">，导师能从社会角色的角度上给我指导和分析，再配合多轮的模拟面试，让我从技能到心态上都更有把握。</em></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">    <br/></p><p>    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">再到“初入职场”，你和前辈同事应该如何打交道？如何尽可能多地学到知识和经验？因为能及时和导师们沟通我的困惑和问题，他们也会给我更多方向、细节和心态上的指导，这一步走得很稳健。</span></p><p>    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></p><p>    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;">    <span style="font-size:18px"><strong style="white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !import