yle="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">1｜本科申研</strong></span><br/>        </p>        <p style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></strong></span>        </p>        <p style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">放弃保研，拿下英美共 10 所名校 offer</span></strong></strong></span>        </p>        <p style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <br/>        </p>        <section>            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">从小我就是一个典型的偏科型选手，数理化不怎么好，但文科成绩一直在班级和年级里名列前茅，高中分科时很自然地便选了文科。</span>        </section>        <p style=""></p>        <section>            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>        </section>        <section>            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">因为早在高考前就想好了要读博，而国内的学界越来越重视海外学习和研究经历，所以决定在硕士阶段就出国留学。</span>        </section>        <section>            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>        </section>        <section>            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">高考结束后选择了在一所重点外语院校就读一个中英结合的文科专业，一是考虑到大城市的外语院校对外交流的平台多，可开阔国际视野，二是这样一个专业既能学习到比一般英语专业更深入的文科专业知识，也能帮助自己不落下英语方面的训练。</span>        </section>        <section>            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>        </section>        <section>            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">此外，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">虽然我的本科母校是所谓的“双非”一本院校，但是录取分数并不低，学生培养质量也很高，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">每一年到英美名校留学、保研/考研到国内顶尖 985 的人数都很多，所以我认为</span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); text-decoration-line: underline; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">出身校固然对于未来的发展很重要，但也不能忽略了自身的努力。</span></strong>        </section>        <section>            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>        </section>        <section>            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我的首选留学国家是美国，原因很简单，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">美国是目前全世界学术的领头军，在那里能够在最优秀的老师的指导下接受最严格的学术训练，学界普遍对美国的学位认可度较高，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">如果能在美国名校取得硕士学位，那么便进可攻克美国顶尖校的 Ph.D.，退可到其他国家和地区的名校继续深造；同时出于对英伦风情的向往，我也作了辅申英国学校的打算。</span>        </section>        <section>            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>        </section>        <section>            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">至于专业方面，由于我的本科专业本身就比较跨学科，所以在考虑硕士阶段的专业选择时也自然而然地把目光投向具备跨学科性质的专业；</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">最后定下申请东亚研究，是因为有一次在朋友圈看到了别人分享的棕榈大道学员的案例分析，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">第一次认识到了这个专业，觉得非常适合自己的需求——我本身就对东亚尤其是中日两国的历史、文学和文化非常感兴趣，而且出于对二次元和日剧的喜爱，还选择了日语作为自己的二外。这也算是最早和棕榈的结缘了，从那时起便</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">开始关注棕榈的公众号，获得了很多干货。</span>        </section>        <section>            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>        </section>        <section>            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">由于我的</span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">规划做得很早，</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">所以</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">大一就开始备考 GRE，有意识地保持一个比较高的 GPA，并且主动去找系里的老师参与课题研究。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">大二时在老师的帮助下获得了港校的 TA 机会，也到博物馆担任了短期的文博助理实习。大三的时候参加了学院的交流项目，到日本交换了一学期，主修日本语言和文学文化，获得了全 A 的成绩单。大学四年期间一共拿过两次一等奖学金、一次全国范围内的文学比赛三等奖，参与过两个国家级的创新项目，并且担任过系里老师的 RA，还参加了联合国的文化交流项目，到大四毕业时 GPA 是专业第一，毕业论文也作为学院优秀论文被推荐到了学校。</span>        </section>        <section>            <br/>        </section>        <p>            <br/>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea7dca49184c5413b6e307e" style="width: 382px; height: 464px;"/></span>        </p>        <section>            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 等线; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;">（大三暑假参加联合国的文化交流项目。</span>            </p>            <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 等线; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;"><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;">图片由棕榈学员提供，未经允许不得转载）</span></span>            </p>            <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 等线; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;"><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><br/></span></span>            </p>            <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 等线; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;"><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><br/></span></span>            </p>            <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 等线; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;"><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"></span></span>            </p>            <section>                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">由于一早就定下了出国读研的目标，于是</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我在大四上学期就果断放弃了本专业唯一一个保研名额。</span>            </section>            <p style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"></p>            <section>                <br/>            </section>            <section>                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我在临近申请季的暑假找到棕榈，成为了棕榈的种子学员。主导师椅子、专业导师 Daisy、班主任 Vivi 和星雨都给了全方面的帮助，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">从申请季时间规划、准备语言成绩，到过往经历的梳理，再到最重要的 PS 的修改，她们全程都尽心尽力地帮忙提供建议，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">等到大四申请季结束时，我一共收获了</span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">英美两国加起来共 10 个名校的 offer，</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">最后经过多方考量，选择了到美国 Top10 之一的杜克大学就读亚洲人文研究项目（MA in Critical Asian Humanities）。</span>            </section>            <section>                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>            </section>            <p></p>            <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 等线; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;"><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><br/></span></span><br/>            </p>            <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">2｜硕士就读</span></strong>            </p>            <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; pad