  <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">杜克大学位于北卡罗来纳州的达勒姆市，校园环境优美，学校建筑有很浓郁的古典气息，校内人文气息也较为浓厚。我就读的 CAH 项目由亚洲与中东研究系开设，以文化研究相关理论训练的强度与深度见长，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">系里的氛围很融洽，师生比很高，老师们都非常 care 学生的个人发展。</span>            </section>            <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: