overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></span>            </p>            <section>                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我在两年硕士期间一共需要修满 30 个课程学分，也就是上 10 门课程，外加撰写一篇 60-70 pages 的毕业论文，并且通过 oral defense，才能够顺利毕业。</span>            </section>            <p style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"></p>            <section>                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>            </section>            <section>                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我在本系共修了 8 门专业课，其中包括一门与硕士导师的 independent study，这门课需要我自己制定研究主题和相关的阅读书目，每周与导师见面一次汇报读书情况，期末再根据自己的研究主题来写一篇课程论文，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我觉得这对于培养学生的自主研究能力与主动性非常有帮助。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">除了在本系选课之外，我还在文学系和文化人类学系各选了1门自己感兴趣的课程。</span>            </section>            <section>                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>            </section>            <section>                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">为了腾出最后一个学期的时间来写毕业论文，我的修课都安排在了前三个学期，每学期上 3-4 门课，平均每周的阅读量是 150-300 页不等，由于大多是晦涩的理论文本，因而往往需要花很长的时间来消化，且每门课都需要交 15-20 pages 的期末论文和进行论文的课堂展示。</span>            </section>            <section>                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>            </section>            <section>                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">读研期间，我在读 reading 和写 paper 的过程中愈发感受到了做学术的乐趣——</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在阅读他人的学术专著时可以不断更新自身的知识体系，同时这一过程中也激发了我很多灵感，促使我产出一些独特的见解，并将这些见解写成逻辑清晰的论文，于是我更加</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">坚定了自己想要读博、继续在学术路上行进的信念。</span>            </section>            <p></p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>            <div style="text-align: center;">                <span style="color:#b2b2b2;font-family:等线"><span style="font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea7dd539184c5413b6e308a" style="width: 587px; height: 283px;"/></span></span>            </div><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; font-family: 等线; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（杜克一景。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">图片由棕榈学员提供，未经允许不得转载）</span>            <p></p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></span>            </p>            <section>                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">美国文科专业的课程基本上都是以 seminar 的形式开展的，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">大家在课前一定要认真读老师布置的 reading，课堂上要积极发言参与讨论，给老师留下比较好的印象，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">这样以后申请时想要找老师写推荐信，才有可能获得强推。比如我的推荐信，除了导师以外，找的推荐人都是我上过他/她的课并且拿了 A 的老师，由于老师们对我印象不错，所以都第一时间答应给我写 strong recommendation。</span>            </section>            <p></p>            <section>                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>            </section>            <section>                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">此外，我在学校上课之余，还在导师的鼓励下</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">积极向各个研究生会议和国际会议投论文，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">到申请季时，一共参加/收稿了 6-7 个会议，也建议有志于读博的同学多参加这样的会议，能够借机结识到专业同好和相关领域内的大牛学者，通过做学术汇报，可以得到同行的反馈与建议，也能够了解到学界内最新潮的话题与研究方向，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">是扩大自己的学术交际圈和增进学识的绝佳途径，这对于申请 Ph.D. 也是大有裨益。</span>            </section>            <p></p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></p>            <div style="text-align: center;">                <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea7dd939184c5413b6e3095" style="width: 501px; height: 305px;"/>            </div>            <p></p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 等线; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;">（在牛津大学出席国际会议时所摄。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 等线; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;">图片由棕榈学员提供，未经允许不得转载）</span>            </p>            <p></p>            <section>                <br/>            </section>            <p></p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">3｜申博</span></strong>            </p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">研究方向的确定</span></span></strong></span></strong>            </p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></span></strong></span></strong>            </p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></span></strong></span></strong>            </p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span></strong></span></strong>            </p>            <section>                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">有志于继续读博深造的同学，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">建议大家最好能在硕士刚入学的时候就明确自己大致的研究兴趣和方向，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">因为说实话虽然美国的硕士项目大多是两年，但是如果不想 Gap 的话就需要在硕士第二年便开始申请 Ph.D.，时间还是很紧凑的，如果能早点定下自己的研究方向就能让一切井井有条一些，也能够基于自己的需要有针对性地去选课。</span>            </section>            <p></p>            <section>                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>            </section>            <section>                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我是在申请硕士的时候就在自己的 PS 里写想要</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">研究东亚近现代知识分子的 cultural identity 以及自我认同的问题，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">尤其是从 gender 的角度切入，我 Ph.D. 申请的材料里写的研究方向也大致落在这个框架里，但是一开始选择的 material 主要还是基于文学文本，等到上了一学期的课以后，深入接触到了西方批评家如阿多诺和本雅明等关于媒介与文化现代性的理论，突然就产生了把跨媒介研究的思路引入到自己 research material 里的想法，于是我的研究计划逐渐开始明晰。</span>            </section>            <section>                <br/>            </section>            <p>                <br/>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea7ddda9184c5413b6e309c" style="width: 524px; height: 365px;"/></span>            </p>            <p></p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></span></strong></span></strong>            </p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 等线; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;">（杜克图书馆的其中一处自习室</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px;">。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 等线; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;">图片由棕榈学员提供，未经允许不得转载）</span>            </p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></span></strong></span></strong>            </p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></span></strong></span></strong>            </p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <br/>            </p>            <section>                <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <strong style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89); white-space: normal; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">4｜申博</span></strong>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"></span></strong></span>                </p>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">选校和 RP/SoP 的撰写</span></span></strong></span>                                </p>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>                <p></p>                <section>                    <br/>                </section>                <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"></span></strong></span>                </p>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">Ph.D. 的申请最看重的是与意向导师的 match 程度，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">如果两人意趣不相投的话，哪怕是那些非 big name 的项目也不一定会录取你，所以我的选校就是从选导师开始。</span>                </section>                <p></p>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>                </section>                <section>                    <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">选意向导师有两种方法，</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">一是最简单直接的，到各个项目的官网去看哪个老师的研究方向与你最接近，但是这种方法也是比较耗费时间精力的；二是在平时的学习中，肯定多少都会读到自己研究方向内比较有名的学者的论文和专著，如果有对自己胃口的老师，那就可以网上搜索一下，看看这些老师如今都在哪些学校、哪些项目就职。</span>                </section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>                </section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我的话采取的就是第二种方法，将自己以前读到过的喜欢的学者的 publication 都简单地分类列举了一下，最终</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">锁定了美国、加拿大和香港共约 12 所学校</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">的 Ph.D. 项目。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">确定了选校 list 之后，就可以发邮件给老师套磁了，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">不过由于文科 Ph.D. 基本上是 committee 决定制，套磁对录取结果的影响其实是微乎其微的，唯一的作用是向老师了解一下这一年对方是否有意向招新的 Ph.D. 学生，有些很 nice 的老师甚至还会告诉你今年系里 funding 的情况，如果遇到老师说今年不招新学生，或者系里因为无法落实 funding 所以暂时不招某个方向的学生（文科专业常遇到的痛），那就可以果断放弃申请该项目，不至于浪费申请费了。</span>                </section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>                </section>                <section>                    <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">Research Proposal（RP）和Statement of Purpose（SoP）是 Ph.D. 申请当中的重中之重，一定要留出足够的时间来准备。</span></strong>                </section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>                </section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">香港和加拿大的学校因为类似于英国学制，要求提交 RP，而美国需要提交 SoP，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">这样一来我就需要同时准备两份差异比较大的材料。RP 的篇幅一般都比较长，比如香港的学校大多要求我提交一份 12-15 pages 的 RP（1.5 倍或双倍行距），加拿大的学校有的要求 RP 的长度为 5 页，而 SoP 的篇幅则更简洁，一般不超过 2 页（double-space）。</span>                </section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>                </section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">RP 相比 SoP 内容会更多更细致，基本上等同于 Ph.D. 论文的开题报告（简短版），一般由 5 个主要部分组成：研究背景与目的介绍、提出的问题假设 or 初步论点 &amp; 每一章节大致的内容、文献综述、研究方法与材料概述、研究的意义。</span>                </section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>                </section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我从去年 6 月底开始确定了 RP 的题目之后，花了近两个月时间搜集相关参考文献，8 月底开始和棕榈配备的专业导师来回沟通，直到 11 月初才正式定稿。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">专导针对 RP 每个部分内容都给我详细讲解了应该如何书写、如何突出要点，每一部分都进行了 2-3 次的深度语音沟通，并且帮我反复修改，到最后定稿时我们双方都对最终版本的 RP 非常满意。</span>                </section>                <section>                    <br/>                </section>                <p>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>                </p>                <p>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea7de309184c5413b6e30a0" style="width: 603px; height: 380px;"/></span>                </p>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 等线; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;">（申请季时RP相关的材料。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 等线; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;"><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;">图片由棕榈学员提供，未经允许不得转载）</span></span>                    </p>                    <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 等线; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;"><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><br/></span></span>                    </p>                    <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 等线; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;"><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><br/></span></span>                    </p>                    <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 等线; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;"><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-family: 等线; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"></span></span>                    </p>                    <section>                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">SoP 相对来说没有 RP 展开得那么深入，主要是要给审阅的 Committee&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">展现自己对某一具体研究方向的理解和掌握情况，然后绘制一个既有创新性又有可行性的 future research scheme。</span>                    </section>                    <p style="color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-size: 14px;"></p>                    <section>                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>                    </section>                    <section>                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在有限的篇幅里，要尽量让 SoP 的语言精炼准确。</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; text-decoration-line: underline; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">首先，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">要开宗明义地表明自己的研究方向是什么，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; text-decoration-line: underline; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">接着</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">可以讲述自己在相关领域的准备，比如上过的哪些课、读过的哪些理论或者文本促使自己对该领域有了怎样更深层的了解，然后可以展开谈论一下自己正在写的硕士论文主要在做哪方面的内容、如何帮助自己深化和明确对未来 Ph.D. 研究的设想。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; text-decoration-line: underline; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">紧接着</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">就是 SoP 的重头戏——future research plan，在这一部分里，要进一步地细化自己的未来研究方向，通过和现有的学界成果对话，阐述自己的研究能够在哪方面补充已有研究的不足之处。这一部分的内容基本上和 RP 的第二、四和五部分是高度重合的，可以相互套用，不过篇幅上需要作相应的删减。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; text-decoration-line: underline; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">最后的 whyschool 部分，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">简单讲一下自己申请该项目的原因、想要跟着哪位/哪几位教授做研究，以及对方学校/项目的资源能够在哪方面为自己的研究提供支持。</span>                    </section>                    <section>                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>                    </section>                    <section>                        <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">最后想和大家说的是：我在追寻学术梦想的路上已经奔跑了很多年，未来的道路也依旧漫长，然而我坚信，</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">志之所趋，无远弗届——与大家共勉，祝所有追梦者都能如愿以偿！</span></strong></span>                    </section>                    <p></p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 10