cing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">拉夫堡大学 材料科学与工程专业</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">        <br/>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <img src="data:image/gif;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVQImWNgYGBgAAAABQABh6FO1AAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; height: 44.55px !important; display: block; transform: rotate(0deg); width: 22px !important;"/>                    </section>                </section>                <section>                    <section>                        <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">“专业不感兴趣+高数挂科”</span></strong>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">        <br/>    </p>    <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我一直想学经济金融相关的专业，但高考英语发挥有点失常，导致我没被心仪的专业录取，最后被录取到了制药工程这个专业。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">刚摆脱高考的“囚笼”，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">没有明确的未来规划，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">再加上高中阶段一直被灌输“上大学就彻底解放了”的错误观念，大一时的我像匹脱缰的野马，将囤积多年的读书压力充分地释放。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">因为对制药工程专业的兴趣不高，所以我对学业不是很上心。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">取而代之的是加入各种各样的社团、学生会，并且时常翘课。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">很快，我尝到了苦果——</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">高数挂科、大一学年的 GPA 还不到 2.0 。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">这样的成绩自然又让我</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">失去了本科转专业的机会。</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"></span>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p>                        <br/>                    </p>                    <section>                        <br/>                    </section>                </section>                <section>                    <section>                        <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">“大好年华，总要拼一把”</span></strong>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">        <br/>    </p>    <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">大一糟糕的学习成绩刺痛了我的神经，我也开始反思：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">这么好的年华，总不能这样混下去，要学到实在的本领和知识。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">所以大二的时候，我开始重视专业课的学习，退掉了社团职务，并且开始思考本科毕业后的发展方向。考虑到国内读研的时间偏长，我决定出国留学。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">        <br/>    </p>    <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead9465ebe5e6316ad749eb"/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">        <br/>    </p>    <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">既然要留学，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">提升 GPA 自然是我的首要任务。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在专业课的学习过程中，我紧跟着老师的上课节奏，做好课堂笔记以及课后复习，认真完成每一次平时作业。将功夫用到平时，让我在期末复习也轻松不少。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">经过大二大三的努力，我成功将 GPA 从 1 点几刷到了 3.1 左右。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">尽管努力了很多，但大一的挂科已然让我的绩点成为硬伤，所以</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">必须要有出色的软背景来弥补，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">当时正巧看到辅导员在群里发的通知——许