rial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">通过朋友的推荐，我认识了棕榈大道。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">仔细对比过三四家留学机构后，我觉得棕榈四对一的辅导模式很吸引人。而且助教在咨询时非常有耐心，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">不仅为我解答了一些基本问题，还在了解具体情况后帮我做出初步的定位，给的建议也很理性中肯。</strong></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在规划选校梯度时，导师先询问我的个人背景和选校意愿，再根据描述的信息去拟定选校表，匹配一些符合条件的学校任我挑选。最后，我们一起商量敲定最终的选校方案。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">当时我选择投递 7 所学校，包括 2 所冲刺、3 所主攻、2 所稳妥。期间有过调整，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">但总体保持择优录取的原则，基本都是我心仪的学校和项目，能兼顾专业排名和院校综排</strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">，也是我中意的偏技术方面的 BA 专业。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">制定了目标后，首先要解决的问题就是标化成绩。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">当初时间比较紧张，却迟迟考不出理想的成绩，我经历过一段非常煎熬的备考时期。</span></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead9190ebe5e6316ad74996" style="width: 632px; height: 461px;"/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(121, 123, 170); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（图片来</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(121, 123, 170); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">源于网络）</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">去年 9-12 月，我基本是一个月雅思、一个月 GRE 这样备考，有时还可能撞在同一个月。分数不理想的话，只能一遍又一遍去考，心态很差的同时效率也不高，一度想要放弃。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我的英语成绩不太好，雅思也是考了好几次才拿到 7.0。最初参加过校外辅导班，但时间非常零散，战线拉了一年左右。每周末都抽出几个小时上课，听起来强度很大，但由于战线太长效率并不高。有时学校突然有什么安排，时间协调不过来，需要请假的次数也很多。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">所以，我建议早考完早安心，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">雅思和 GRE 这种考试不能把战线拉太长</span>。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">最好能专门留出一段时间专心准备一个考试，等需要成绩的时候才不至于措手不及。</strong></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在备考期间要保证熟练度，尤其是听力和阅读，尽量每天都要练习。口语要准备自己的素材库，不能照搬和硬背其他素材。写作跟四六级考试也不同，更注重行文的逻辑性，重在把意思表达清楚而不是塞语法。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead91a1ebe5e6316ad7499a" style="width: 618px; height: 437px;"/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear