gin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">记得罗格斯大学有一个题目，它要求写一个</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">在专业方面进退两难的经历</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">，我不太理解这道题的意思苦恼无从下笔，专业导师 Ben 师兄就举了很多生活中的案例，听完之后我恍然大悟，然后我把工作中碰到的一次报账经历告诉导师，他点拨我如何巧妙地结合这段经历，既体现自己的专业性同时秉持职场上的道德操守。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">还有主导师&nbsp;Phoenix 同样功不可没，她对学生特别尽责特别了不起，最忙的时候深夜 2-3 点还在改文书。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(39, 168, 169); font-size: 14px;">一开</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">始我写的内容略显平淡，几段实习也是不知名公司的普通职位没有什么亮点可言，然而经过导师的辅导，文书里融入了耳目一新的叙述技巧，可读性大大提升</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(39, 168, 169); font-size: 14px;">了。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"></span><br/>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(254, 254, 254); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(39, 168, 169); font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">虐心的面试</span></strong></span>                        </p>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">面试对商科生来说是另外一个至关重要的环节，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">Ben 师兄</span>首先为我安排了一次测试，考察我的答题水平，结果让我大吃一惊，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">导师指出我目前有太多的问题需要改进了</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">，然后详细地告诉我每一个问题应该怎么回答，我就认认真真地全部记下来。之后我花了两周的时间，每天看每天读，把所有的面试要点背得滚瓜烂熟。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">到了正式面试的前一刻，主导师&nbsp;Phoenix 为我安排了最后一次模拟面试，提出一些比较犀利的问题，然后告诉我可以从哪些角度作答，要尽量结合个人经历表现地自然一点。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">在福特汉姆大学的视频面试中，面试官一脸严肃的表情不免令我有点小紧张，不过好在很多问题我已经做好了充足的准备，所以总体来说面试进行得很顺利。面试结束后，Phoenix 建议我给面试官发一封邮件，内容大概是“我觉得今天和你的交谈很愉悦，希望有一个好的结果……”就连这样细小的事情Phoenix 导师都考虑得十分周全了，有她在我超安心的。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead8ce8ebe5e6316ad748fe" style="width: 646px; height: 476px;"/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: