     </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">大一的时候我在我们学校的可口可乐俱乐部做干事，参加了俱乐部里的一个比赛，当时那个比赛有一些 HR 和经理来做评委，后来因为在那场比赛的表现给评委留下了很不错的印象，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">其中一个 HR 创业的时候就来找到我，所以我很幸运的在大一就加入了这个创业团队。</span></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);"><br/></span></span>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead86aaebe5e6316ad74845" style="width: 615px; height: 404px;"/></span></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);"><br/></span></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">这段创业经历对于当时刚步入大学的我来说收获是非常大的，因为<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">我是团队里年龄最小的成员，所以通过跟其他学长学姐的接触我学到了很多做事的方法和技巧，</span>在社交等方面他们也给我起了很好的示范作用，相当于是为我后面整个大学的规划奠定了一个基础吧。</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">大二是我的一个转折，在专业老师的支持下，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">当时我和几个同学一起建立了我们学校的 Rotaract Club 扶青团，</span>通过这个组织我接触到了很多国际项目，比如<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">中英商会等</span>，以及一些国际志愿者的资源，在这过程中<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">我基本上都是在跟外国人打交道</span>，这些体验让我看待事物的视野变得更宽阔，心态也更加开放，这段经历也更加坚定了我想要出国体验新环境，融入国际化氛围的想法。</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead86c2ebe5e6316ad7484c" style="width: 610px; height: 437px;"/></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">大三的时候<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">我在我们学校主办了 TEDx 年度大会</span>，作为一个 leader 我需要全权掌控活动，这对我来说挑战还是挺大的，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">比如我要去找演讲者找场地，讨论演讲主题与内容，谈赞助等等，</span>各个细节都要去把握，这也算是我大学期间对我锻炼很大的一段经历，它提升了我的综合能力，比如领导力、紧急事故的处理、流程监管等，同时<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">通过这个活动我也获得了很多资源</span>，认识了非常多优秀的人，学到了很多东西，对我之后的人生规划产生了一些思考。</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center;">                    <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead86dbebe5e6316ad74853" style="width: 620px; height: 366px;"/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">诚然，有得必有失，我因为做太多的实习社团等活动导致雅思等标化成绩不是很好，这是让我在申请时比较苦恼的一点，其实应该早一点注重这些考试成绩的，另外让我比较遗憾的是我没有利用我们项目的特性去交换一下，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">整个 4 年都是在国内读的</span>，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">虽然有英本的学位，但我并没有真正切身体验过英国教学，</span>这也让我之后更加期待去英国接受更加纯正的英式教育，体验英国的文化氛围。</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead86eeebe5e6316ad74859" style="width: 619px; height: 417px;"/></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <section>                    <section>                        <section></section>                        <section></section>                        <section></section>                        <section>                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">申请这一路</strong>                        </section>                        <section></section>                        <section></section>                        <section></section>                    </section>                </section>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我跟棕榈一直都挺有缘分的，因为大学前几年社交活动比较多，大二参加一个叫创业周末的活动时，当时<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">小组内的一个小姐姐是从事教育行业的，她就向我推荐了棕榈。</span>后来大三在组织我们学校的 TEDx 活动时，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">棕榈的人也为我推荐表演嘉宾等</span>，一来二往也对棕榈产生了比较好的印象，所以最后就是签的棕榈。</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section></section>                                <section>                                    <p class="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                        前期辅导                                    </p>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">因为我是<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">从管理学转到金融</span>，其实在申请时是会有一些限制的，比如有些金融硕士项目会要求本科是财务、数学等专业，再加上<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">我没有考 GMAT，其他标化成绩也不是很出色，所以我在选校时也和两位导师讨论了很久，如何扬长避短</span>，切忌一些自杀式行为。</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead8702ebe5e6316ad7485f" style="width: 617px; height: 421px;"/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我的主导师<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">兜兜姐</span>给我介绍了很多学校的具体要求和项目信息，向我<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">科普一些学校的招生偏好和课程设置</span>，比如帝国理工会更喜欢数理背景更好的学生，而我在这一部分很欠缺，所以挑战很大。比如 LSE 会偏向学术较好、理论研究出彩的学生，这就要求我多积累一些论文等。再比如墨尔本大学可能会比较在乎学习排名等等这些信息都是兜兜姐告诉我的，对我确定最终选校名单帮助非常大。</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">具体到一些学校的某个项目时，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">兜兜姐也会不断用一些过往案例来帮我判断，</span>告诉我以前申到这个项目的学生大概是什么情况，成绩背景如何，同时也会跟我分享那个学生写文书的经验等，这种跟过往学生作比对的机会其实是很难得的。</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead871cebe5e6316ad74865" style="width: 547px; height: 1341px;"/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(165, 170, 194);">（兜兜导师与学员聊天截图）</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">另外因为是转专业申请，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">兜兜姐也会让我多去关注一些金融相关的新闻、资料、网课等，鼓励我从实习方面入手</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">，比如寒暑假应该去投哪些方面的实习，是偏技术类或偏分析类的等，像我当时有一个国金证券的实习本来是不太敢去争取的，这个实习含金量较高，对学生的本科有一定的要求，后来兜兜姐说没关系不管怎样还是可以去尝试一下，最后也成功得到了这个机会。同时兜兜姐还会鼓励我去学习很多技能如 C 语言等，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">让我从各个渠道以各种方式提升专业背景。</span><br/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section></section>                                <section>                                    <p class="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                        文书成长                                    </p>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">最开始写文书的时候在梳理经历这一块其实花了一些功夫，因为我虽然之前做了很多实习，但其实与金融没有很大的关联，对于申请而言含金量并不高，所以后来<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">和专业导师讨论过后她就建议我以证券公司实习的经历作为重点来串联</span>，从银行开始入手，到证券越做越熟练，以此展示我个人具有很明确的职业发展目标。因为<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">专业导师告诉我很多学校在招收学生时会很看重学生在这个学校毕业后能不能有一个很好的发展，</span>对学生个人素质这方面会要求较高，所以专业导师就让我要在文书中要重点突出相关的经历和能力。</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead8736ebe5e6316ad7486a" style="width: 592px; height: 442px;"/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">在写文书的过程中，两位导师都给了我很多宝贵的建议，她们会尽可能的<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">把我之前做的一些 project 与学校项目的课程设置等做一个更好的匹配</span>。比如当时兜兜姐看我比较缺乏 Quantitative skill ，就让我用<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">竞赛</span>经历所展现的投资性分析等能力去弥补，通过我在竞赛中做商业决策时所体现的一些如收集数据等长处来展现我自学能力较强，同时<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">凸显我在金融方面的 motivation</span>&nbsp;等。</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">另外兜兜姐也提醒我要在文书中体现一些思考，比如我的一些实习要反思在那个阶段有什么不足，后来又如何去改正提升等，整篇文书下来能体现出我是一个有态度有思考且具备一定能力有目标的学生，是有血有肉的，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">并不是冷冰冰的一个加长版简历</span>，所以我对最后的成稿是非常满意的。</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75