 box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">整个申请下来我觉得<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">最大的收获就是写作能力的提升</span>，这也是我一开始选择棕榈的一个很大的原因，我始终认为，文书初稿要由我自己来写，这样完成的内容才真正贴上了我的标签，独属于我个人的。我不太喜欢有一些其他的中介让老师来全权包办文书的这种模式。</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我觉得棕榈的导师一直都在教我怎么写好一篇文书，帮我做出修改为我提出建议， 因为我是英制教育，所以需要写很多论文和资料，当我写完文书再去完成这些时我能<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">明显感觉到我的逻辑思维能力变强了，写作技巧的运用也更加得心应手，这个收获是我之前没有想到的。</span></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead8761ebe5e6316ad74871" style="width: 591px; height: 420px;"/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">同时我也逐渐学会了如何去分辨好文书和差文书，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">后来</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">我也有帮一些申请美国的朋友写文书，</span>因为他们觉得他们的中介写的文书不是很好，我完成后交给他们时，他们也都觉得我改的很不错，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(224, 73, 67);">我觉得这也算是棕榈培养我的一种能力吧，</span>让我真正懂得了好文书的技巧和方法，这样我才能去帮助别人。<br/></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                            