ter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">关于潜力，我觉得我一直在不断地激发自己。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">大二时我有过一天连续考 3 门 final 的经历，考了整整 9 个小时，</span>因为当时必须上完这 3 门课才能按时毕业，虽然行程非常紧凑，但我只能迎上前去抗，最后虽然熬下来了但那 3 门课的成绩并不理想，一门 C+ 两门A-，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">那也是我 GPA 最低的一个学期，只有 3.1 左右。</span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></span>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead83e8ebe5e6316ad747fe" style="width: 548px; height: 381px;"/></span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">后来几年，我一直在奋起直追，尤其是</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">去年 6 月份 的 final week，可以说是我大学四年来最拼的一段时间，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">我当时还在做小组 project，本来是 6 个人的小组，有 3 个人临时跑了，导致最后我们 1 个人要做 2 个人的工作，同时我还要应对其他课程的考试。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">这个 data analysis 课的 final project 的主题是&quot;matching donors to projects&quot;，就是一个根据某些捐赠群体的特性去自动分配给各个需要不同捐赠金额的项目。因为用普通的 regression model 达不到预测的效果，所以我必须去自学&nbsp;machine learning 及更深的 R programming 。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我花了很多时间去上网搜索，积极向助教咨询，同时把握好教授的上班时间抓紧询问等。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">最后我选中了 2 种具备一定优势的模型和其他组员一起完成了这个 project，整个过程虽然很艰辛，但收获非常大。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">我记得在</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">赶 data analysis 课的 final project 头一天，周四下午我刚考完一门课的 final，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">然后第二天周五做这个项目一直做到晚上 12 点,&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">中间只睡了 3 个小时。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">周六上午搬家干苦力，下午出发坐飞机回中国，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">回国后第二天就开始实习。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">这种高强度的拼命经历可以说是我目前为止</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">最 intense 的 schedule</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">，我觉得自己那段时间真的很刚，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">最后我的付出也得到了回报</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">，那个学期我的 GPA 达到了 3.93。</span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></span>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead8409ebe5e6316ad74809" style="width: 541px; height: 374px;"/></span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0p