          <section>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;">捧着哥大的 offer，恍惚让我想到了当时梦想去港大的那个“小白”的自己。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;">本科学财务的我一直梦想能申到港大的金融项目，小心翼翼地不敢把金数放进自己的规划里。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span><br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;">了解这个项目的都知道，港大是众多商科申请者的梦校，金融项目又比较偏好有工作经验的申请者。在申请季前，我兜兜转转找了好几家留学机构，都建议我增加一些保底校，觉得以我的背景去申请成功率不高，不过我一直坚信通过努力，梦想并不是遥不可及。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;">偶然间发现高我一届的学长正在棕榈的帮助下申请，最后成功收获了港大的金融 offer。有了他的真实案例，我也咨询了棕榈的导师，对自己的背景有了明确的定位，知道自己的硬软性条件和港校是匹配的，有很大的希望，终于信心十足和棕榈一起向第一轮申请进发~</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead80b8ebe5e6316ad747d4" style="width: 555px; height: 368px;"/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;"></span>                    </p>                    <section>                        <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em;">                            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;">了解金融项目的小伙伴都知道，金融在美国 Top 30 学校里开设得很少。所以选校阶段，我们确定了两个主方向：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">金融和 BA，共选了十所学校。而 number 1 的位置上我们定的是哥大的金数项目。</span>                        </p>                        <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em;">                            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                        </p>                    </section>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;">刚开始选校的时候，因为家人和自己都一直有藤校的情结，想试试冲刺申请哥大的项目，但对申请高难度的金数项目犹豫不决。首先我本科并不是数学这种数理背景突出的专业，也没有编程背景。但考虑到自身想从事资产管理类工作的职业目标，不管是哥大的藤校光环还是金数项目本身的硬核课程，都会对我未来的职业规划道路有很大的帮助，因此即使机会渺茫，也一直没有放弃这个可能。</span>                    </p>                    <section>                        <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em;">                            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span><br/>                        </p>                    </section>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;">导师综合考量了我的背景，结合经验告诉我是有希望的，可以放手一搏，于是我们把哥大定为我的冲刺校。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section>                                        <section>                                            <section>                                                <section>                                                    <section>                                                        <img class="" src="data:image/gif;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVQImWNgYGBgAAAABQABh6FO1AAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; height: 20.5px !important; vertical-align: middle; width: 40px !important;"/>                                                    </section>                                                </section>                                            </section>                                        </section>                                    </section>                                </section>                                <section>                                    <section>                                        <section>                                            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">重新认识自己的感觉很奇妙</strong>                                            </p>                                        </section>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">最开始用”素材挖掘器”来整合自己过去的经历，感觉超奇妙。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);">在过去的经历中 ，很多细节亮点其实很容易被遗忘，但通过挖掘让我又加深了对经历的了解和总结</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);">，虽然过程烧脑，但是这让我第一次完整地认识了自己。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">后来整个写文书、简历、推荐信的过程，我都可以感受到自己能力上明显的进步和提升。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">记得第一篇文书返稿的时候，文件一打开就是满满的“红色”，密密麻麻的都是导师的修订痕迹，特别壮观哈哈。但经验和技巧就是在这反复斟酌和修改中积累起来的，写到最后几篇文书的时候，导师特别骄傲地夸我已经掌握了文书写作的技巧，都不怎么需要修改了。现在回头看，真的特别庆幸自己完整参与了整个文书写作，意义远不止申请本身了。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: