important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px;">虽然对于等待的焦虑记忆深刻，但那段日子导师对我的陪伴也让我觉得特别温暖。我基本上每天都要微信轰炸我的主导师，问她各种我遇到的问题。她真的是人美声甜又耐心负责的小仙女，每一篇文书的修改都很专业，而且认真把握申请中的每一个细节，特别值得信任。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;<br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px;">在后来的流程里，由于相互的信任，我们配合的非常默契。不管是文书写作的问题还是心态上的不稳定，我都会第一时间想到和她交流，申请季共同的奋斗早就让我们友谊的小船变巨轮了。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead80e4ebe5e6316ad747d8" style="width: 538px; height: 414px;"/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px;">当然，心态的调整是建立在自信的基础上的，其实就是需要在申请之前做好充分的准备，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">强烈建议同学们要提前加强自己的编程背景。</span>因为我申请季开始时已经大四了，来不及修学校的相关课程，所以在导师的推荐下在网课平台补了 Python&nbsp; 和 R 语言等课程，积累了一定的编程基础。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">其次量化相关的实习对于金数金工类项目的申请也是很重要的，并且一定要有意识的去挖掘自己的工作内容。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px;">我暑期在证券固定收益部实习的时候，由于刚接触的工作不太涉及量化，导师了解后就建议我多和带我的老师交流，了解他们的投资逻辑和模型，并充分利用手头的资源去学习量化的知识。其实每一个项目甚至任务背后都有可以挖掘的宝贵经验。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px;">所以小伙伴们在找实习的时候，一定不要盲目追求数量，而要多和职场前辈或者学长学姐讨论，明确自己的目标，知道这段实习对自身的意义是什么。当你在挖掘工作内容，思考总结实习中得到的收获后，已经为你的文书积累了素材。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">再一次感到庆幸，专业导师的指导让我一直走在对的方向上，事半功倍~</span></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead80fcebe5e6316ad747e1" style="width: 549px; height: 406px;"/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !impo