word !important; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我大一上学期的 GPA 只有 3.19</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">，那时候刚进大学，对学习完全不上心，基本上就是浪了半年。后来到了大一下，发现身边的同学大家都开始渐渐在意 GPA ，每个人都很拼，再加上我又读的是 2＋2 的项目，想着之后要在国外读研，以现在这个 GPA 根本去不了我心目中的好学校，所以受种种因素的影响，我<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">大一下</span>就开始发愤图强，没想到一下子就<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">把我的 GPA 提升到了 3.94</span>，当时我就觉得，不逼自己一把真不知道潜力可以有多大。</span></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></span>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead7b5febe5e6316ad7479f" style="width: 592px; height: 373px;"/></span></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;">这个努力的过程说起来容易做起来很难，因为我读的是 2＋2 的项目，虽然当时是在国内上学，但整个教学体系都是按照国外来的，包括授课的老师也是外教。现在回想起来我当时做的比较好的一点就是</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">每次有什么不懂的就去老师的 office hour，那时候我基本上天天都往老师办公室跑。</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;">当时有一个农经的老师，office hour 特别满，提问的同学超级多，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">每次为了问一个问题差不多要排上2、3 个小时的队，但为了提高成绩我也愿意，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;">其实这门课原本并不是我擅长的，但最后出来的成绩我非常满意。</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;"><br/></span>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead7b83ebe5e6316ad747a5" style="width: 597px; height: 400px;"/></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;"><br/></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">我想补充一点，虽然我们是 2＋2 的项目，但当时因为还在国内上学，所以评分都是按照国内学校的评分机制来的，而<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">这个机制对拿 A 的同学是有名额限制的，</span>所以为了不让自己即使高分都被刷下来，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我拼到一定要保证自己每次作业都是满分或高分，一定要争当第一名，这样对于拿 A 才比较稳妥。</span></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">我一直觉得提高学习成绩上课听讲是最基础的一步，而下课去问老师则是最关键的一步，你不能保证每次上课的内容都能完全消化，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">对我来说提升 GPA 帮助最大的就是一次次 office hour 的收获，</span>我是属于那种有一点点不懂得都会去问，不管会花费我多少时间。而且在我看来哪怕全懂了你也可以去问，多和老师沟通想法，不管是对这门课的体会还是对学习的困惑都可以聊，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">因为这个过程能给老师留下好印象，对于拿高分也大有裨益。</span></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></span>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead7ba1ebe5e6316ad747ac" style="width: 596px; height: 436px;"/></span></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></span>                </p>                <section>                    <section>                        <section></section>                        <section></section>                        <section></section>                        <section>                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">水到渠成的申请</strong>                        </section>                        <section></section>                        <section></section>                        <section></section>                    </section>                </section>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169); border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(39, 168, 169); border-top-color: rgb(39, 168, 169); border-right-color: rgb(39, 168, 169); border-left-color: rgb(39, 168, 169); text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span class="" style="margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 4px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; border-radius: 80% 100% 90% 20%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: block; float: left; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">1</span><strong class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 2px; display: inline-block;"><div style="text-align: left;">                            <strong class="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">选校</strong>                        </div></strong>                    </p>                </section><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">&nbsp;</span>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">之所以想要转专业申请生统/统计等主要有 2 个原因，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">一是我很喜欢数理化方面的东西，</span>通过本科的学习，我发现农经这种偏文科的课程我并不喜欢也不擅长，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">二是我想要之后留美工作，</span>按照现在的大环境趋势，在美国找与数据分析等偏理科性质的工作相对来说会比较容易，就业岗位也很多，所以<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我其实是在确定了职业规划后有目的性地去选择申请专业与选校的。</span></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></span>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead7be1ebe5e6316ad747b1" style="width: 602px; height: 417px;"/></span></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我最后决定<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">主申生统辅申统计</span>，因为当时我的主导师 CY 姐 跟我说虽然我的背景也有偏统计的部分，但<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">想要冲刺更好的学校可以侧重申生统，</span>这样把握可能会更大，同时她也建议我在申生统时可以<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">选择一些综排较高的学校</span>，对留美工作也有一定帮助，最后确定学校 list 很顺利，因为我自己之前做过调查，CY 姐也有<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">给我一些棕榈过往案例的 Excel</span>，通过看一些<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">与我背景差不多的同学申了哪些学校</span>，基本上也能很快确定下来名单。</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead7bfdebe5e6316ad747b6" style="width: 597px; height: 438px;"/></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; 