ction>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我觉得我的<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">主导师 CY 姐&nbsp;</span>除了在申请上的辅导外，对我最大的一个帮助就是<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">陪伴</span>。尤其是之前大四上为了补充数理背景我要上 7 门与数学统计相关的课，还要备考 GRE，又要忙申请的事，压力特别大。</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我当时基本上是靠咖啡熬过，最高纪录是<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">一周瘦了 7 斤</span>，整个人特别累又很焦虑，然后 CY 姐就一直鼓励，我有什么烦恼都会跟她说，她每次都会<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">回我很长很长的文字或语音</span>，哪怕是在她的休息时间甚至<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">半夜 12 点</span>。我有</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">时候都会</span>开玩笑说感觉她也挺不容易的，接了我这么一个总在“骚扰”她的学生。</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-w