rtant; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; caret-color: red;">相反当时棕榈接待我的 sales 学姐每次都回答得特别详细，比如我问她一些关于申请的时间线是怎样的，或是我的背景应该如何提升等问题，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; caret-color: red; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">她都会回我又长又详细的信息，</span>告诉我应该怎么做等，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; caret-color: red; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">因为当时我并没有签约，所以我觉得能做到这种程度真的非常感动，</span>而且当时我人在美国，还有时差，所以也是这种态度打动了，我一回国就直接去北京办公室咨询了。</span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; caret-color: red;"><br/></span>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; caret-color: red;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead7e90ebe5e6316ad747c8" style="width: 599px; height: 417px;"/></span>                </p>                <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: bo