   </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">金融女恋上理工男</span></strong>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">大学给我的初印象是个欢脱的游乐场，逃离了老师和家长的管束，我可以任意参加自己喜欢的社团和活动。四年里带给我最多美好回忆的要数 KAB 创业俱乐部，记得大二那会《大鱼海棠》电影上映不久，导演梁旋来我们学校做巡回宣讲，我和社团的小 Q 一起承接了这个活动。从大一懵懂的小部员到成长为独当一面的部长，这次活动带给我的磨砺特别多，活动之后我和小 Q 恋爱了！</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead786bebe5e6316ad74766" style="width: 572px; height: 522px;"/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我是商学院的金融女，他是工程学院的理工男。我们时常会坐在星空下的草地上幻想未来，将来的路其实无外乎 4 个方向：出国、保研、考研或者工作。我是一个喜欢尝试新鲜事物的人，不喜欢把自己固封在一个地方，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">不管是考研还是保研都是在国内读书，这样的环境和本科没有什么区别，反而让我有种读了 6 年本科的感觉</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">；与其这样不如出国看看，体验国外的学习氛围和生活方式，而且在这件事情上小 Q 的想法和我一拍即合，那就一起出国吧！</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <br/>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(39, 168, 169); letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 16px;">托福从&nbsp;93 到 110 的咸鱼翻身</span></strong>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"></span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">介于我的英语底子很差，从大二开始我就准备&nbsp;GT 了，第一次托福考试惨的不行，93 分。我咬咬牙又发奋复习了半年，97 分，才提了 4 分……好像不论我怎么努力，托福都上不了 100，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">眼看着申请季逼近，我的内心已然崩溃了，一崩溃我还止不住地想哭。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">那段备受煎熬的日子里我几乎每天都要哭，而且不止一次。有时候在晚上空无一人的自习室里，我一边拿着手机背单词，眼泪一边就像决堤似地流了下来；在小 Q 面前我哭的次数就更多了，现在想想又好气又好笑，有时候去食堂的路上小 Q 一转头发现我人没了，然后就看见我蹲在地上放声大哭。沉重的心理压力让我变得敏感又脆弱，但哭诉完、心理压力释放完之后我还是会继续埋头苦学英语。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead78bcebe5e6316ad7476e" style="width: 571px; height: 550px;"/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">17 年和 18 年的真题我反复看了 N 遍，阅读、口语、听力和写作也都反复练习了 N 遍，如果再考不出来的话，我感觉已经没有东西值得再复习了。</span>到了 18 年 5.12 号的第三次托福考试，我怀着无比忐忑的心情走进了考场，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">最后出来的分数竟然有 110 分！更惊喜的是，两周后 5.27 号的 GRE 考试我拿到了 330 分</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">，艰难的时光总算熬过来了，功夫不负有心人！</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169); font-size: 16px;">确定申请方向</span></strong>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">为了冲刺更好的梦校，我和小 Q 一起走访了许多家留学机构，其中棕榈给我的感觉是非常靠谱、负责的一家。他们的咨询小哥哥向我展示的后台系统特别高级，包含非常完善的学生和导师的信息系统，此外还有和我申请方向特别匹配的经验丰富的主导师和专业导师，多番比对之后我确定下来就选棕榈了~</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">BA 是我希望主申的方向，它是当下美国很火的复合 Master 专业，一门编程、数据分析和商科相交叉的学科，和我本科的专业跨度不是那么大，既可以学到新的编程技能，未来的就业面也非常广泛。但和棕榈导师们诊断定位后，我发现自己的弱势在于编程背景不够强，研究经历也不太够；另一方面残酷的现实情况是：美国的 BA 硕士项目申请一年比一年火，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">光是我加的留学群就有计算机、数学等其他专业的同学来申请 BA，竞争着实惨烈啊</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">！考虑到我的统计与编程相关的课程修得比较少，在申请偏 tech 的 BA 项目时不太占优势，因此选课时导师们给了我诸多意见以强化个人的编程和数学背景。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead78dcebe5e6316ad74775" style="width: 568px; height: 512px;"/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <br/>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(39, 168, 169); font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">简历，实习的敲门砖</span></strong></span>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">主导师和专业导师的简历辅导也十分给力，她们帮我修改了好几版的中英文简历，导师们用数字量化了我在实习中的工作成果，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">修改后简历的逻辑看起来更清晰了，和我原始的版本相比，真的是把简历从普通提升到了高级。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">从大二暑假到大三，我尝试了几段不同的实习，有光大银行的贷款助理以及安永会计事务所的审计实习生。再后来挑选实习的时候，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">导师们建议我把主要精力放在有助于申请的项目上，我会把比较满意的职位发给导师们审核，然后导师们 pass 掉很多不太匹配的职位</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead7907ebe5e6316ad7477b" style="width: 567px; height: 526px;"/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"></span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">今日头条和亚马逊的数据分析岗是我后来找到的为申请重磅加码的两段实习，尤其是我从去年末就职的亚马逊，它是美国影响力最大的电子商务公司之一。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">在这份实习中我和 manager 成了非常好的朋友，我是处女座，她是双鱼座，我们俩非常合得来~</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">而且谈起留学我们俩超有共鸣的，她之前在美国的波士顿读完了 MBA，回国后在亚马逊工作。她不仅和我分享了国外学习的见闻，更教给我工作中为人处世的道理，让我对未来增添了许多信心。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(39, 168, 169); font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">面试&nbsp;who 怕 who</span></strong></span>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">和梦校的招生官在线面试，而且全程英文面试对我来说是一个不小的挑战，不过还好有专业导师来辅导模拟面试。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">一开始我准备的内容比较 general，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">而专导作为一个久经职场的面试老手，她会抠非常细致的点来提问，而且不按常理出牌</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">。比如一般的面试问题有：你最喜欢哪段实习？你最难忘的是哪段实习？但专导会问我：你最讨厌哪一段实习？搞得我都懵圈了。在导师的启发下，我运用了安永的那段实习，由于我当时做的是金融审计工作，这是一份比较循规蹈矩的工作，要求从业者细心、认真的特点，但无法激发人创新的 idea，因此这份工作并不适合我的性格，也不是我未来发展的方向。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead7932ebe5e6316ad74780" style="width: 571px; height: 509px;"/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">后来在正式面试的前一天，主导师又为我模拟了一次全英文的面试。到了第二天的正式面试，因为我之前准备十分充足了，也就没那么紧张了，总体来说发挥地非常顺利。</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <br/>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">文书，及时作调整</span></strong></span>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">辅导我文书的主导师人超 nice，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">她是一位性格温柔、耐心而且经常鼓励学生的导师</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">。尽管她 base 在美国，但基本上每次我发消息她神速地回复了。包括遇到一些突发问题，比如网申出了点状况国内的导师都休息了，而她会及时地出来解决问题，是一种让人特别安心的存在。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">去年 9 月初我和主导师约了文书课，掌握写作技巧后我从中文的提纲开始写，然后完成英文的初稿，交给导师点评修改，接着导师返给我重新优化，这样来回 N 遍后最终定稿，导师的文书写作功底要比我强太多了，优化后的文书提升了不止一个 level~</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead795febe5e6316ad74785" style="width: 573px; height: 487px;"/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我总共写了两个版本的文书，第一版是去年 9 月份完成的，第二个版本是在我拿到亚马逊的实习后大概 12 月末完成的，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">它在第一版文书的基础上语言更加丰满了，逻辑结构也更加严谨了，几位文书导师功不可没</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">。拿着第二版文书我分别申请了 CMU、UT Austin、UCLA 和哥大这 4 所大神级的学校，其中 UT Austin 是全美 BA 专排第 2 的学校，仅次于 MIT</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">（</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">2018年 QS 排名</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">）</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">，课程设置非常硬核，而且我的偶像——生活大爆炸的男主 Sheldon 14 岁就在这里上学了，如果能中这所学校那简直跟做梦一样不可思议。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <br/>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169); font-size: 16px;">从保底校到梦校 Offer 的大逆转</span></strong>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"></span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">等待 Offer 的日子实在太煎熬了，第一轮申请我总共投递了 5 所学校，有杜克、南加大、艾默里、罗彻斯特和华盛顿大学。原本我以为第一轮申请的人比较少，竞争可能会小一些，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">但我太天真了，除了罗彻斯特大学的 Offer，其余 4 所学校全都发来拒信</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">！分析了一下第一轮申请的人普遍比较优秀，而且好多学校第一轮偏向招海本和有工作经验的人多一些，被拒也就不奇怪了。不过，这 4 封拒信给到我的沉重一击，因为后面申请的几所学校难度还要更高，心中涌起一股申请季要凉凉的不祥预感。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">看到我的战绩不是很好，人也非常沮丧，主导师发来一长段话安慰我，鼓励我“没有关系，我们还有其他学校，你肯定能拿到好的录取结果，不要放弃！”，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">导师对我毫无保留的信任，让我重拾起信心，用优化后的第二版文书投完剩下的几所学校。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead7994ebe5e6316ad7478b" style="width: 532px; height: 639px;"/>&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">经历了漫长的等待，再次接到 Offer 是 2.26 号的清晨，当时我睡眼惺忪地从床上爬起，点开邮件看到正文里一个大写的 Congratulations，我整个人“腾”的一下就起来了，再仔细一看学校居然是 CMU！我心中向往的大神级学校，别提有多开心了！</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">3.10 号幸运再次降临。那天早上我在实习的路上收到了 UT Austin 的邮件，正文大概写着结果已经出来，点击下方的链接查看。 我心里突然咯噔一下，预感这个项目可能没有希望了，毕竟 UT Austin 招的人本来就少，上一届才录取了十几名中国学生，如果这是封 Offer 的话应该直接写结果了吧……我怀着无比忐忑的心情点开了链</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">接，居然跳出了录取的字样！</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">简直像中了头等彩票一样，我实在不敢相信自己就是那个幸运的锦鲤！</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">而且与我并肩奋斗的男友小 Q 也拿到了 UT Austin 的 Offer，未来我们很有可能去同一所学校圆梦，没有什么比这更幸福的事情了！</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ead79afebe5e6316ad7478d" style="width: 552px; height: 461px;"/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; 