 border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(20, 86, 86); border-top-color: rgb(20, 86, 86); border-right-color: rgb(20, 86, 86); border-left-color: rgb(20, 86, 86); border-radius: 3px; line-height: 36px; background: rgb(39, 168, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2 次大陆第 1 名</span></strong></span>                </section>            </section>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">单独把考证列出来是因为备考&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">CIMA （特许管理会计师公会）</span>是大学这几年花费我较多时间精力的一件事，虽然这个证了解的人可能并不是很多，但我还是选择去攻下这道难关。我经历了 2 次案例考试（运营级和管理级），为了备考我差不多要消化 2000 页左右的资料，复习强度非常大，最后老天没有辜负我的付出，<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2 次考试我都取得了大陆第 1 名的成绩。</span></strong></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></strong></span>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5eaa5513ae50ef62882ffeb8" style="width: 547px; height: 422px;"/></span></strong></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">（学员 CIMA 证书）</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">为什么会选择去考这个证？<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">这个证书是英国颁布的，它是一个影响力较大的国际通用组织，</span>如果在申请学校时我能拿到这样一个官方的认证，是对我自身实力的一个绝佳证明，在我看来<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">这是比学科成绩含金量更高的</span>，尤其是在取得了第 1 名的好成绩之后，能够更好地说明我比别人更有竞争力，可以<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">向申请学校展现我在案例分析能力和财务知识等方面都比别人掌握得更好</span>，基于这样一个良好的积累，我也能在研究生阶段比他人更好地学习金融知识等，这对我的申请助力是非常大的。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="" style="margin: 0px 7px 11px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(20, 86, 86); border-top-color: rgb(20, 86, 86); border-right-color: rgb(20, 86, 86); border-left-color: rgb(20, 86, 86); border-radius: 3px; line-height: 36px; background: rgb(39, 168, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">死磕拼成专业第 2</span></strong></span>                </section>            </section>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">在学习上，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我是那种任何时间段都不会放松 GPA 的人</span>，为什么会把自己逼这么紧？除了因为它对申请至关重要，还因为我曾高考失利。我高中读的实验班，身边的同学都去了很好的学校。当读大学后感受到因为双非背景在出国等很多方面都不占优势时，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我就发誓不能再一次输给别人那么多，</span>我要加倍努力和那些 211、985 的学生站在同一起跑线上。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 16px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5eaa5522ae50ef62882ffebb" style="width: 470px; height: 455px;"/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-size: 13.3333px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（整整一箱备考时写掉的笔记）</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">几乎在每个学期开始前我都会<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">提前制定好我的整体计划</span>，哪几个月应该完成什么大目标（如 GMAT 考试等），在完成大目标时我还会制定日计划周计划等等，不像别人在考试前一个月或前一周才开始复习，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">每次期末考试我基本上都会提前 2 个月开始梳理复习</span>整个学期的知识。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">除了时间上的付出，效率也非常关键，想要高效就得对自己够狠。我在决定某段时间要学习后就会<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">卸载手机里面所有的娱乐软件</span>，只留下沟通必备的微信和学习软件。而且学习时我一定是把手机扣过来的，不会回复任何微信信息，只有需要相关软件时才会使用。其实我每天学习时间也就 7、8 个小时，和很多人比不算长，但在这几个小时内我不绝会让自己分心，并且一定要把提前安排的任务完成。最终通过这些付出，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我申请时的 GPA 达到了 91.36，位列专业第 2、年级前1%。</span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5eaa5534ae50ef62882ffec1"/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="" style="margin: 0px 7px 11px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(20, 86, 86); border-top-color: rgb(20, 86, 86); border-right-color: rgb(20, 86, 86); border-left-color: rgb(20, 86, 86); border-radius: 3px; line-height: 36px; background: rgb(39, 168, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">别样挖掘社团经历</span></strong></span>                </section>            </section>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">社团是我大学生活中必不可少的一环，外联部、志愿者部我都待过，不过要说收获最多的还是<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">辩论社的经历</span>。值得一提的是这段经历乍一看对留学申请来说没什么直接的助力，因为我当上了社长，可以在文书中展现一下领导力，但这一点相对来说比较普遍。后来和<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">主导师 CL 姐讨论后她觉得还可以凸显一下我对时事的关注</span>。因为我有和她分享之前做过的一些辩题，通过涉及的内容等，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">她觉得还可以深挖我对新闻政策的跟进与分析，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">毕竟申请金融的话这方面的资质也是一个重要的加分点。所以<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">通过 CL 姐的独辟蹊径最后辩论社经历也成为我申请材料上的一个亮点。</span></span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="" style="margin: 0px 7px 11px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(20, 86, 86); border-top-color: rgb(20, 86, 86); border-right-color: rgb(20, 86, 86); border-left-color: rgb(20, 86, 86); border-radius: 3px; line-height: 36px; background: rgb(39, 168, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">收获最大的金融实习</span></strong></span>                </section>            </section>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">当然要申请金融，还是要有相关背景的实习才能更有优势。以前我其实是不知道做什么样的实习对申请帮助才会比较大，虽然在 2 家公司做过财务实习生但都没怎么接触核心业务，后来签约了棕榈通过与 CL 姐打电话，她建议我应该做一些金融方面的实习，所以<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在大三暑假我去了<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">中国金融期货交易所</strong>，在下面一个资金管理小组做估值。</span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5eaa5545ae50ef62882ffec7" style="width: 559px; height: 435px;"/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">这段经历是我收获最大的一段实习，当时有很多上海 985 院校的金融毕业生在那里工作，他们给我分享了很多实用经验，也是在那里<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我第一次切实知道了基金投资的整个运作，认清金融行业的实际操作等，</span>不管是对我丰富简历还是个人发展都非常有利。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="" style="margin: 0px 7px 11px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(20, 86, 86); border-top-color: rgb(20, 86, 86); border-right-color: rgb(20, 86, 86); border-left-color: rgb(20, 86, 86); border-radius: 3px; line-height: 36px; background: rgb(39, 168, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">数字化展现简历</span></strong></span>                </section>            </section>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">由于我的各种经历较多，自己又想把所有经历都呈现在简历中，导致最初呈现出来的简历效果很差，基本上就是属于罗列工作内容，显得很宽泛。后来&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">CL&nbsp;姐和专业导师就教我要学会</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">数字化展现简历</span></strong>，比如把一个大概的东西具体写成我做了 13 个基金的估值，分别种类是什么。而且当时这个工作是上午出信息下午就出结果，我每天都需要在拿到结果的 1 个小时内把估值做出来，所以<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: red; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">导师就让我着重把这方面加进去以体现我的工作效率</span>，且这 1 个小时内完成的量也比较大，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">导师也会让我把这些量具体怎么完成的都全部展现出来，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">通过这样数字化+具体化的呈现，我的简历就显得丰富又具体。</span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5eaa5565ae50ef62882ffece" style="width: 565px; height: 438px;"/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="" style="margin: 0px 7px 11px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(20, 86, 86); border-top-color: rgb(20, 86, 86); border-right-color: rgb(20, 86, 86); border-left-color: rgb(20, 86, 86); border-radius: 3px; line-height: 36px; background: rgb(39, 168, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;2 篇精彩文书的指导</span></strong></span>                </section>            </section>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">在我的申请文书中，有 2 个是比较特殊的，一个是约翰霍普金斯的，另一个是圣路易斯华盛顿的。JHU 当时给出的文书要求是要从人性的角度（business in humanity）去考虑企业未来的发展，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">针对这个主题我和 2 位导师专门开了一个半小时的会来讨论。</span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">因为我本科是会计，会计其实是需要学很多公司治理和职业道德标准的，导师们就鼓励我在文书中先说一下我在本科会计的学习中接受了很多职业道德教育，并且我相信在未来的金融市场或者商业环境里这种标准是一直被需要的，最后<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我强调了无论以后是从事会计还是金融相关的行业，我都会很注重人性这方面，</span>会在未来践行已经学到的这些品德，约束自我。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">导师们告诉我通过把本科所学与未来规划结合起来，切中文书的主题要求，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">这样呈现出来的效果会更有说服力，更易受青睐。</span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5eaa557bae50ef62882ffed3" style="width: 585px; height: 415px;"/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">另一个</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;WUSTL 的文书则要求我去思考未来的金融是什么样的</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">，在写文书前导师们先鼓励我自己先去想一些主题，我自己想的是资管新规，因为当时我在中金所实习，我认为新规出来后可能会带来一些变化，和导师们开完讨论会后她们先肯定了我在这方面的想法，但<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">导师们也跟我强调这个文书的要求重点是未来的变化，而新规已经形成了，再去写可能发挥空间不是太大。</span></span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">所以<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">导师们就给我提供了好几个新的思路</span>，比如可以从金博会入手，或是写中美贸易谈判下是否会有新转机等，经过一番讨论后我最后选中了<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">中美贸易这个主题</span>，定好后<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"