ify; position: relative; z-index: 0; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; visibility: visible;">    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">“我一直觉得耶鲁离我很遥远，除了清北，我想也许其他高校的很多同学多少会有点这种感觉吧。”</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">Zeke 说起他申请之初的心情，觉得能够中一个北美前 30 的硕士就很开心了，而现在他已经决定拒掉耶鲁的 offer，开始自己的博士攻读之旅……</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">学员故事</span></strong></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></strong></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5eaa53c0ae50ef62882ffe89" style="width: 190px; height: 203px;"/></span></strong></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;">Zeke</span><br/>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">北京航空航天大学 生物与医学工程</span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">GPA：3.79</span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">收获offer：</span></strong></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">华盛顿大学 博士</span>                    </p><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"><div style="text-align: center;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">伊利诺伊大学厄巴纳-香槟分校&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">博士</span>                    </div></span>                </section>                <section>                    <div style="text-align: center;">                        <span style="font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);">普渡大学 博士</span>                    </div>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">耶鲁大学 硕士</span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">约翰霍普金斯大学 硕士</span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">加利福尼亚大学洛杉矶分校 硕士</span><br/>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">卡耐基梅隆大学 硕士</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section>                                        <section>                                            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                                <br/>                                            </p>                                        </section>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                    <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">一个神奇的堪比CS的专业</strong>                                </p>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">对于出国，开始我是抱着申硕士的目标去的，我的 GPA、英语成绩都不错，但并没有很好的科研经历，更别提成果了，当时的目标就是拿下一个美国排名前 30 的硕士。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">没想到最后根据导师的指导，我选择了硕博混申~ 最后还申到了美国排名前 20 的博士，也收到了导师当时建议、鼓励我去申请的耶鲁硕士的 offer，开心之余想想真的很奇妙。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">生物医学工程（BME）是怎样一种存在？我想专业领域内的小伙伴都知道，它在美国是很有前景的，在国内也是朝阳产业。为什么这么说呢？首先生物医学工程在美国是很热门的专业，很多想学医的硕士都会选择 BME 专业，在科研上优势很大。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5eaa53d6ae50ef62882ffe93" style="width: 598px; height: 441px;"/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">就业方面，BME 主要产业是医疗器械，在美国收入很高，甚至堪比 CS。健康一直是人类关注的重点嘛，医疗技术也与生活质量息息相关、随着经济的发展，人类必然越来越重视这一块，需求量会越来越大。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">在人工智能发展的时代，医疗与 AI、计算机结合得越来越紧密，BME 下的许多分支和 CS 是互通的。比如我认识不少清华的博士学长，学医学图像处理相关专业，毕业后很多都去了人工智能领域，找到的工作都很不错。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">相比发达国家，BME 在国内还在发展之中，没有 CS 那么热门，但我很看好它的前景。随着我们国家的经济发展，BME 必然越来越厉害~</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section>                                        <section>                                            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                                <br/>                                            </p>                                        </section>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                    <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">本科直博，跑赢时间</strong>                                </p>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">和棕榈的结识说来很巧，我爸一位同事家的孩子也在棕榈做申请，强烈向我老爸安利棕榈，我就去了线下办公室和老师面对面聊了一下，当然感觉很好，才有了现在的申请故事~ 我选的是半 DIY 辅导，这样自己的参与感更高，能更多地掌控文书的脉络，毕竟是为自己申请，还是要把主动权抓在你自己手上才对~</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5eaa53e9ae50ef62882ffe9a" style="width: 599px; height: 444px;"/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">刚开始我和导师针对三维背景对我做了定位和选校，我的绩点与英语成绩是突出的优势，但科研经历比较少，也没发过文章，和发过文章的同学一比较，申博让我觉得很忐忑，所以一直抱着“先申到一个 TOP 30 的硕士项目就很满意了”的心态。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">我的导师在分析了我的背景之后，鼓励我去尝试博士。他说：“申请博士并不是一定要你有多么丰富的研究成果，本科直博想出 paper 是很难的，这个大家都知道，这不是最核心的，最重要的是你的潜力与动机。” 同时他也推荐了耶鲁的BME硕士项目给我，告诉我以我的背景是可以尝试的。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">最后也证明这是这步棋我走得很正确，真的很感谢导师了~ 我一直有读博的打算，现在直博等于帮我节省了很多时间成本，少走了弯路，可以说跑赢了时间~</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5eaa53ffae50ef62882ffea0" style="width: 597px; height: 421px;"/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">虽然科研是弱项，但我也有积极弥补。在文书中对我的课程作业、毕业设计都作了详细的描述，这需要对文书结构有一个专业的把控和分析，所以导师辅导我花了很多心思。也通过文书向招生官展示了我的研究能力，弥补了我没发文章的短板。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">在申请过程中我对自己的面试表现也挺满意，我觉得也是我能拿到 PhD offer&nbsp; 的一个关键因素。记得面试华盛顿大学 PhD 项目的时候，教授问我：“为什么要读博”（相信这个问题对博士申请非常重要），我很清晰地阐述了自己的读博动机，对创造性的追求等等，最后教授还笑得蛮开心，看得出得到了他的认可~</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">能有这样的结果也得益于自己充分的准备，主导师发了很多华盛顿大学的项目材料、面经、各种 sample 给我，我都一个个认真学习准备。也给我做了模拟面试，告诉我面试哪些雷区不能踩，让我学到了不少技巧。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section>                                        <section>                                            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                                <br/>                                            </p>                                        </section>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                    <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">别因麻烦放弃你的冲刺校！</strong>                                </p>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88);">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">硕博混申是一条挺“艰巨”的路，比只申硕士当然要复杂一些。选校的时候，硕士项目你会选择不同的梯度，到了博士项目又要重头再来好好选一遍，同时还要套磁、面试，压力是不小，但我依旧觉得非常值得。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5eaa5416ae50ef62882ffea3" style="width: 598px; height: 416px;"/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">一般来说只要你科学选校，充分准备，硕博混申的结果都不会太差，我还有些更牛的同学混申了 20 多所，最后总会中几所。 当然混申多所学校，你需要花费更多的精力来准备不同学校的文书、申请材料。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">套磁当然是博士申请的关键一环，我当时邮件联系了项目的秘书，他们都建议我赶紧去联系项目教授。我把要申请博士的每所学校的相关教授资料都看了，挑选出我感兴趣的课题，并且在招人的，筛选信息的工作量是巨大的。那会儿记得每天都在做这件事，学校里的课业也不能放下，所以每天都是连轴转的状态，基本也没什么玩的时间。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">我的套磁也开始得晚，到了九月份申请季才开始准备，为啥开始得这么晚呢，因为我大三放飞了自己一整个暑假~ 也是因为大三时语言考试考得挺累，所以暑假就好好放松了。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">这也是我第一个给申请的小伙伴们的建议：还是尽早准备吧，语言要更早开始准备，早点考出来，你大三就可以开始进入申请工作，更游刃有余了。不要像我一样，套磁和申请同步开始，有的套磁甚至更晚，现在想想也是为自己捏了一把汗。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <img class="rich_pages  __bg_gif" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/PI7nB3LiaicmQSBmBia7ovrDS3chqsrAoiaLPEykvbyenojxl6zibJNsvcTPv2RaoicMN0W11KMYwplLwqW54ow9RsoA/640?wx_fmt=gif&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; width: 377px !important; visibility: visible !important;"/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: