g: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">加利福尼亚大学洛杉矶分校</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">西北大学</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">哥伦比亚大学</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">宾夕法尼亚大学</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">纽约大学</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;">Final Decision</span></strong></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">斯坦福大学</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section>                                        <section>                                            <section>                                                <section>                                                    <section>                                                        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">绩点科研二三谈</strong>                                                        </p>                                                    </section>                                                </section>                                            </section>                                        </section>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">3.95，将近满绩的 GPA 是我申请的一个有力武器。在申请美国本科的时候，我 GPA 就不太高，硕士可以说全面开启了考霸模式，对于考试拿高分这件事还是比较拿手的~ 但科研方面就弱了些，不像一些科研大神可以出 paper、出成果。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">我的本科实习比较少，科研也是校内科研，可以说丰富但不优秀，没有出什么成果和 paper。当然了，本科做科研想出结果是很难的，这个不可否认，但并不代表你不用在意科研。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">大三暑假时我开始准备申请，导师测评了我的背景经历，说我科研经历较少，最后一学期还是有时间，抓紧时间再补充一下。所以即使开学要准备初期申请还有各种课业，我还是咬咬牙去做了两份科研，最后也证明这个决定很正确~</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5eaa51c2ae50ef62882ffe63" style="width: 553px; height: 361px;"/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">GPA 在申请中的地位很重要，有些申请案例中甚至占了一半的优势。但你同样会发现有些 GPA 一般般，也被名校录了的同学，他们就是软性条件超级牛，比如超神的科研经历、突出的比赛经历等等。如果你和我一样 gpa 比较好，但是科研背景比较薄弱，我觉得到最后去弥补一下也是来得及的。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">对于科研，我觉得要保持这样一个正确的心态：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">科研态度积极，科研结果随缘。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">导师一直鼓励我：“本科生想做出科研成果确实很难，能发 paper 的更少，关键是重在参与！” 如果你觉得自己科研能力一般，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">不要因此放弃，多多参与，以量取胜，突出自己的科研态度和潜力。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section>                                        <section>                                            <section>                                                <section>                                                    <section>                                                        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">时而信心十足，时而忐忑不安</strong>                                                        </p>                                                    </section>                                                </section>                                            </section>                                        </section>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">我的导师是美国机械工程的 PhD 毕业，作为“行内人”他对这个领域了解得很深入，有他的把控我的过程大致上可以说是比较顺利的，只是内心时而信心百倍、时而忐忑不安，可以说挣扎了好一番~</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <img class="rich_pages  __bg_gif" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/PI7nB3LiaicmSErmUsfzibmziafCKqPHD0ovd9tpp38IHfAYj3WDhYQaqx03krWNtEo8cP7cHHt4hl3dNA5iawpdVdw/640?wx_fmt=gif&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; width: 245px !important; visibility: visible !important;"/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">当时导师和我经过深入的讨论和定位，将斯坦福和 MIT 作为我的冲刺校，这两个学校在我看来遥不可及又触手可及……这种感觉是最折磨人的，有时纠结自己会不会定位过高，需要增加几所保底校，不然得“全聚德”。压力是不可避免的。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">但导师的专业度让我很信任他，让我相信我的选校 list 是客观可靠的，所以一直勇敢往前走。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">我这个人还有点强迫症，也很固执，如果老师说的话没道理我会完全忽视。而我导师说的话我都能听得进去，并且认真执行~因为我能感受到他的专业与负责，毕竟他是走过这条路的人，给出的建议都很有道理，很中肯。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">如果要说导师给我印象最深的辅导，应该是文书上了，有了申请本科的教训，虽然我不怎么喜欢写作，但是这写文书也是做足了功夫。和导师的文书课就上了两节，再在各大官网上看学校的研究实验室信息，有没有和我契合的课题，都可能是我文书的素材。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5eaa51d5ae50ef62882ffe6c" style="width: 553px; height: 393px;"/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">一个有强迫症的人写文书一定要一口气写完，不能中断，所以就造成了好几个通宵的夜晚，再不断返稿给导师修改……当然，一切都是值得的。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">MIT 和哥大都给我发来了面试邀请，我发现招生官对申请者的经历和项目的了解是很看重的，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">他们希望找职业导向非常明确的人，所以一定要明确你为什么要申请这个项目。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">充分的准备也让我的面试很流畅，导师提前给了我面经，辅导了面试的注意事项，最后就算面试的问题不在面经里，我也能回答得非常流畅~</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section>                                        <section>                                            <section>                                                <section>                                                    <section>                                                        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">美本与陆本，各有烦恼</strong>                                                        </p>                                                    </section>                                                </section>                                            </section>                                        </section>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">在申请前，我就咨询了很多学长学姐，RPI 的同学蛮多都是棕榈的“过来人”，他们给我推荐了棕榈。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">对于美本的学生来说，选校与文书是最需要人来辅导帮助的，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">很多双专业、转专业的同学，要做好一个方向的“选择题”需要慎重再慎重，这毕竟决定了你之后的就业方向~</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">同时美本很多专业课业压力也非常大，尤其是最后一年各种事情要忙，有导师的辅导我想能有双重的保障，保证自己游刃有余地 handle 好各种任务。有时候我们总是自信爆棚，觉得自己都能拿下，但当所有任务都堆积过来才发现人的精力有限，特别容易顾此失彼。如果因为这样丢掉了本可以到手的 offer，那真是“生命不可承受之痛”了……</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5eaa51f3ae50ef62882ffe6f" style="width: 560px; height: 435px;"/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">对于国内本科的小伙伴来说，除去信息不对称、资源不对等等问题，我觉得最吃亏的是你的 GPA 是否受到认可。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">很多 985/211 的小伙伴都有这种感觉，其实自己学校在国内牌子不错，但大多数美国人都不了解，所以很多时候你的成绩单信用度会打折扣。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">这时候招生官会着重看重你的软背景了，实习、科研、文书等等成了关键因素。我知道国内的实验室资源、科研氛围相比美国要弱一些，资源也有限，想做出成绩难上加难。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">但不要轻言放弃呀，我建议陆本的小伙伴们更加重视起科研的机会，抓住可以去美国交换的机会，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">不管是暑期的大学交换、校内科研项目或者美国公司的暑期实习生，都放开手去申请，对你软背景的提升有很大的帮助~ 同时如果交换的项目能够抵学分，你交换的成绩更能增强成绩单的可信度。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <img class=" __bg_gif" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/PI7nB3LiaicmSErmUsfzibmziafCKqPHD0ovfkptJz8n5t4NGNiauc1O8rGnUOJEebBbibPUTBv8Nm7qnVic5CbKic6X3w/640?wx_fmt=gif&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; width: 175px !important; visibility: visible !important;"/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;">所以多看多听多搜索吧，不要让进步的机会从自己手边溜走，当你付出了心力去完成申请这件事，结果总会是“情理之中”的！</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 1px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 18px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; widows: 1;">你是否也有一个名校梦？</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin: 0px 0.5em; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(88, 88, 88); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 18px; widows: 1; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: borde