 color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"/>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; letter-spacing: 0.4352px; line-height: 21.76px; widows: 1; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <br/>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">放弃上戏导演系，赴北电圆梦</span></strong>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">法国电影大师让·皮埃尔·梅尔维尔说：“我坚信，你必须疯狂的热爱电影才能够拍电影。”在进入北京电影学院之前，我已经具备了拍电影的必要条件：一个狂热的影迷。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">记得小学的时候第一次在大荧幕前看《指环王3》，我就被影片中气势恢宏的画面强烈地震撼了，至此之后我完全沉溺于电影的世界，为搜罗一部喜爱的电影挨家挨户地把碟店翻了个遍，电影相关的杂志、书籍从不放过……再后来面临高考，我没有把 985、211 当作奋斗目标，成为一名电影人才是我的全部追求~</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">北电、上戏、中传的导演系考试我一一报名了，上戏我拿到全国第 7 ，中传的考试也过关了，遗憾的是北电的导演系考试我没能闯入最后一轮，只通过了它制片与市场专业的考试。即便如此，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">我仍坚定地认为北电是离电影梦更近的地方，即便去了制片与市场专业我依然可以接触到热爱的电影创作</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">，换个角度看，电影制作也是中国电影产业里非常缺失的一部分，在北电我必将学有所获。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(39, 168, 169); font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在北电读书是一种怎样的体验？</span></strong></span>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">大多数人提起北电最先想到的就是它的表演系，外表光鲜的演员和明星们自带流量属性，话题不断。大学期间我曾作为本科生的招生志愿者参与学校的招生接待任务，被分配到女生公寓 2 号楼负责新生的入住办理工作。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">凑巧的是在我工作第二天的下午，关晓彤亲自来 2 号楼办理入住，她的身边簇拥着一批工作人员以及各大娱乐媒体的记者，现场的热情立马被粉丝们的尖叫声点燃了。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">零距离的和当红小鲜花对视搞得我难免有些小紧张，关晓彤本人还是非常有礼貌的，亲切地称呼我”师哥“，很快顺利地办完了入住手续。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">除了热门的表演系，北电有超过 10 个院系，文学系、导演系、影视技术系、美术学院、管理系等等，每个院系都有它独特的地方。北电学生的构成也颇为丰富，拿我们寝室来说，你可以看到上铺的男生在读马丁·海德格尔而下铺的男生打游戏的清奇画风，每位北电同学性格鲜明，不过大家都有一个共同的特点：对电影艺术创作饱含热情。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea9a088ae50ef62882ff994" style="width: 611px; height: 374px;"/></span>    </p>    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">在注重实践的北电，我从大一下开始接触到短片拍摄的作业。有一回老师要求我们拍摄一部 5 分钟无台词的并且大、全、中、近、特这几个景别都要有的短片，这对我来说是一个前所未有的挑战，因为那会儿我对电影制作体系还不熟悉，而老师的题目一上来就不简单。我冥思苦想许久，构建了一个恐怖短片的剧本，这样一来既可以规避台词，也可以用各种镜头拍摄一系列的灵异事件，最后短片的完成度不错并且拿了高分。</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">到了大二，学院为我们提供去横店影视基地的社会实践活动，千奇百怪的服装、道具、布景完全向我们开放，给我们极大的创作空间，在那里我分别指导了一部短片和主演了一部短片。横店之行结束后我回到本专业的学习状态，陆续担任了爱奇艺的网剧、网大的制片人工作，离真正的影视制作更近了一步。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea9a0abae50ef62882ff99a" style="width: 614px; height: 405px;"/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">其实影视制作是一个痛并快乐着的过程，你没法预测拍摄期间会出现什么幺蛾子，有时候只能随机应变，死马当活马医。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">比如拍摄一场雨戏，你原本安排在某一天结果那天偏偏不下雨，这个问题怎么处理？亦或是你在某个街道拍片，刚好碰到街道戒严，那怎么与政府人员沟通？诸如此类的问题都需要制片人协调好，不然整个剧组一天的成本就要空转了，损失可能是几十万，也可能是上百万。因此，与电影创作者不同的地方在于制片人的思维方式需要更为成熟，制片人更像是电影工业化体系下的一个人。</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">在大三跟过一些商业项目后，我发现中国电影业的制片人才还处于相对匮乏的状态，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">这体现在国内一些剧组的拍摄计划制定的不完善与不科学，存在产生时间低效、人员浪费、资源浪费等等不良现象。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我所接触到的影视工作人员大多工作非常辛苦，有时候开机拍摄意味着连续 3 天没有任何的睡眠，身心极度的劳累与疲惫。在我看来很多事情是可以规避和改进的，前提是电影的拍摄、策划、发行、放映等环节做到足够的工业化和标准化，目前来说这方面做得最好的可能是好莱坞了。吸取美国电影业先进的地方，学习对方的优势然后琢磨出一套适合中国电影业的方法，是我渴望去美国读研的强大动力。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea9a0c8ae50ef62882ff9a0" style="width: 606px; height: 422px;"/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"></span><br/>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(39, 168, 169); font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">决胜第一步</span></strong></span>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">确定申请前我总以为有大把的时间可以挥霍，一直到大三下我才发现托福成绩没有考，外加一大堆申请材料需要准备，时间明显不够用了</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">，我随即决定寻找相关的留学机构辅助申请。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">一开始我找了名声比较大的中介，他们宣传有专门针对电影专业学生的作品集辅导。我仔细做了一番调研，前后至少约谈了 5 家机构但都非常失望，种种的不靠谱让我放弃了这些机构。后来我刷到棕榈大道，并且去棕榈的北京总部试聊，我觉得棕榈导师的专业度很高，关键是导师对学生抱着非常负责任的态度，没有天花乱坠的宣传而是针对我的个人情况把她们能够做的地方解释地明明白白，我欠缺的东西正好是导师们可以帮到我的，因此我放心地把自己交给了棕榈。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <br/>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(39, 168, 169); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">三维成绩</span></strong>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我对英语学习非常不感冒，但托福又是申请中必须进行的一步，没有办法只能硬着头皮考。要命的是我准备托福的时间非常有限，去年 9 月 30 号我确定下来在棕榈做辅导，接下来的 3 个月有一大批学校的 DDL 要赶，别提有多虐心了。我总共考了 4 次托福，最好的一次成绩仅仅刚挨着 100 分的保底线，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">给我安慰的是棕榈导师们觉得影响不大，鼓励我安心做好作品集、文书等材料的准备工作。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">在专业成绩方面我保持的还不错，GPA 3.83/4 。平日里我保持着一周至少看 3-4 部电影的频率，包括去拉片</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(178, 178, 178);">（一格一格地看电影，深度解读电影）</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">，完了去图书馆看一些电影专业的书籍，制片管理、院线经营管理、影视投融资等占分较大的专业课我也花了很多心思去学。如果你能够真正地热爱电影这么艺术，那么你自然会很投入地学习，成绩也就是水到渠成的事儿了。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea9a0e8ae50ef62882ff9a6" style="width: 632px; height: 409px;"/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <br/>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">选校策略</span></strong>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我的选校是颇为顺利和成功的。首先我确定了 4-5 所最想申的学校，有哥大、NYU、查普曼大学等，然后棕榈主导师 eve 花了很多时间做调研，专业导师 Vicky 根据她的经验提供建议，两人又为我加上了几所不错的学校，比如洛约拉马利蒙特大学、雪城大学等等。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">从学校的综合排名来看我们选的 8 所学校是错落有致的，分为三个档次，但是在专业领域上这些学校都是非常好的学校，每一所学校都有它的优势。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);"><br/></span>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169); font-size: 16px;">文书+作品集</span></strong>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">完成选校后就是让人头大的文书了，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">3 个月要提交 8 所学校的文书，挨得最近的是 UCLA 11 月 1 号的 DDL，这过程堪比好莱坞大片里的生死营救般惊心动魄。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">主导和专导的存在就像是影片中点醒主角的关键人物，她们给到我非常高效的辅导建议，帮助我迅速地推进文书。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">导师们先是花了大量的时间挖掘我过往的人生经历，探讨我的哪些小故事可以挖掘出有效的素材组织到文书里，然后我们再沟通文章的结构框架怎么安排，如何提纲挈领地布局一篇文书。接下来由我写完初稿交给主导修改，导师的第一遍返稿上布满了密密麻麻的修改痕迹，每一行都有详细的批注，拿到稿子我内心是崩溃的，熬夜和一顿苦改是逃不了的。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">但与此同时，主导也在熬夜加班加点地优化文书，她的敬业和负责给了我支撑下去的勇气。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea9a12fae50ef62882ff9ab" style="width: 533px; height: 843px;"/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">除了文书，作品集是电影专业申请中非常必要的一部分。每个学校的作品集要求不尽相同，要根据它们的题目分别准备，这是相当消耗时间和精力的。一般来说，作品集的要求有两个维度，第一个维度是学校要求的短片作品，这个我在大学期间积累了不少的作品可以现用；第二个是学校官网上出的题目，比如 UCLA 要求写一个 10 分钟左右的短篇大纲，这就需要我赶在 DDL 前完成原创作品。要不是 eve 导师主动承担修改作品集的结构和语言，让文字读起来更加的通顺、平滑，更像美国人的表达方式，我恐怕很难用英语把自己的想法表述完整。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <br/>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169); font-size: 16px;">简历+面试</span></strong>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我的简历起初是比较渣的，上完简历课后我才知道一份优秀的简历就像完成一件作品一样，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">需要精心地编排和打磨，每一行、每一列应该填什么样的内容，应该怎样构成，怎么排版都是有讲究的</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">。主导非常细致地辅导我一遍遍修改，前后多达 6 次返稿，有时候短短的一句话要改上好几遍，每一次优化后文字变得更加的精炼和专业了。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">面试对我来说又是一个大挑战，此前我连用英语和外国人长时间对话的经历都没有，更别说用英语流利地应付招生官的提问了。主导和专业导师宽慰我的同时，采用模拟面试的方法和我演练，紧急提升我的口语能力，消除了我的压力和恐惧感，到正式面试时我流畅自如地应对了招生官的提问。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"></span><br/>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169); font-size: 16px;">申请 3 个月，感冒 3 个月</span></strong>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">到了申请后期，我明显有点力不从心了，一方面熬夜不断，另一方面从去年 10 月初我就一直在感冒，身体已经完全透支了。以至于去年 12 月初申请完 UCLA、USC 和 NYU 之后，我和 eve 导师认真地聊了聊，有点想放弃后面学校的申请了。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">Eve 导师的耐心鼓励重新点燃了我的斗志，她希望我能坚持下去，不要放弃每一个机会。后来 eve 导师也感冒了，她硬是扛了下来陪我做完其余 5 所学校的申请，把我感动的稀里哗啦的。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">申请结束后我迎来了漫长的中场休息，从今年 1 月份到 3 月份我的邮箱一片死寂，没有任何的offer/waiting list，甚至连拒信都没有一封，搞得我一度怀疑自己给错了邮箱地址。从一些论坛上我发现今年的 offer 普遍发的比较晚，这和美国电影专业申请人数增多、竞争变激烈不无关系，比如查普曼大学就声称往年给面试者发 offer 的比例是 45%，今年只有 20%。近几年中国电影产业飞速发展，方方面面都需要专业人才，因此导致很多本科是电影及非电影类专业的同学申请读研，在今年达到申请人数上的大爆发。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);">从焦灼的等待到看淡录取结果，我已经做好“全聚德”的打算了，失败了就去工作吧。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">3 月 8 号，我和往常一样在图书馆自习，邮箱里突然冒出一封新邮件，点开一看居然是洛约拉马利蒙特大学的 offer</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(178, 178, 178);">（MFA 项</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(178, 178, 178);">目，Film and Television Production）</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">！我心中按捺不住一阵狂喜，怕自己在做梦还冲去卫生间洗了把脸，确认这是真的不是梦境。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea9a160ae50ef62882ff9ae" style="width: 650px; height: 385px;"/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">如果说第一封 offer 让我免去了失学的痛苦，那么第二封 offer 带来的则是爆棚的幸福感。3 月 22 号我接到一个来自美国的陌生电话，当时我正匆忙地赶路，幸亏没有把号码拉黑，对方居然是哥大的人，他通知我被录取了</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(178, 178, 178);">（MFA 项目，Film Creative Producing）</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">，并且附加 15,000 刀/学期的奖学金！这一刻简直太美好了，春意正浓，阳光很温柔，周围的一切看起来充满了希望。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">哥大这个项目的好处在于电影制作和制片两方面的内容都有包含，我可以继续学习喜欢的电影制作，同时在制片方面提升自己，此外哥大商学院的课程是对我这个专业开放的，这也是一个非常珍贵的机会。从就业的角度来看，一方面国内现在缺乏好的制片人，另一方面未来中美电影产业的合作会越来越丰富，中间存在大量的机会。好好运用哥大的资源，我相信一定能学有所获，不虚此行。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <br/>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(39, 168, 169);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">写在最后</span></strong></span>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span><br/>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">要说有什么值得分享的申请经验话，我想提醒大家，电影专业的申请千万不要拖太晚，因为要准备的东西实在太多太复杂了，每一所学校我都卡在 DDL 前一天递交的，没有任何多余的时间空隙，身体都被掏空了。其次，选对导师特别重要，假如满分是A的话，我的几位棕榈导师都是&nbsp; A++，她们不仅辅导效率高而且心思细腻，耐心又温柔，遇到她们我真的太幸运了~但凡走错一步，我的申请可能不会有 happy ending 了。</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">最后我想对有志于投身电影行业的同学们说，真诚的热爱是支撑你未来几十年走下去的全部动力。或许你能成为一个故事的讲述者，或者是一部电影的创作者，因此你怎么想、怎么做很重要。不受外界因素的干扰，永葆初心，真诚地对待你的事业，它才能给你好的反馈，灵感才不会枯竭。如梦光影的背后隐藏的是众多电影人默默无闻的辛勤付出，而你，准备好成为其中之一了吗？</span>    </p>    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>    </p>    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !importan