idth: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea99ba5ae50ef62882ff924" style="width: 634px; height: 419px;"/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(165, 170, 194); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（“BISU DAILY”比赛照片）</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-size: 13.3333px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="" style="margin: 0px 7px 11px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(20, 85, 87); border-top-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-right-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-left-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-radius: 3px; line-height: 36px; background: rgb(40, 167, 169);">初次实习体验</span></strong></span>                </section>            </section>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">大二寒假，我开始了第一份实习，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在北京人民广播电台《教育面对面》栏目组做实习生</span>，能够争取到这个实习机会花了我很多时间精力，因为过去他们找实习生基本上都是找 985 高校的学生，以我的背景直接申请机会是非常渺茫的。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">我在高中的时候就曾和这个电台经常互动，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">大一时我上过这个电台的培训班，担任过班长，</span>也因此与那里的老师关系更近一步，后来又去参加过几次直播，一来二往和工作人员等都很熟悉了，最后因为我的表现一直很不错，他们给了我实习的名额。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">这个争取到实习、从零到一的过程我在申请学校的材料中也有凸显出来，以此体现出我擅于发现和利用身边的资源。</span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">我当时负责的工作有三方面：运营公众号、参与直播及其辅助工作、设计图标制作节目预告等。说道制作预告这是我在春节时临时接到的一个任务，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">挑战在于我只有 2 天的时间准备</span>，而且我之前一直只是写文章做直播，没有相关经验，但最后我还是高质量的完成了。所以后来<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在准备申请部分学校的 supplemental essay 中我也有写上这段经历，以展示出我具备良好的危机处理能力和临时解决问题的能力。</span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0