           <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">这段实习对我拿到哥大的 offer 帮助很大，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">因为我申请的是哥大的Communication and Education 方向，是教育与传播项目，而在这份实习中<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我既有传播的经验也有教育的经历</span>，尤其因为这个平台的资源很好，我还有机会与一些教育公司的 CEO 探讨教育政策等，所以不管是传播还是教育两方面我收获都很大，这些对申请的帮助是显而易见的。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">值得一提的是，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">当时负责我申请的棕榈专业导师正好也是哥大这个专业的学姐</span>，在申请文书中，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">她为我增添了很多本土化的气息，比如有让我阐述一些哥大的校园活动，为我讲解一些项目信息让我能更加了解</span>，以至于写文书时能对症下药，所以能成功拿到哥大 offer 离不开她的付出。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">除了哥大，这段实习对我申请波士顿大学的Communication/Journalism,Marketing 帮助也很大，因为在工作内容中会涉及到与很多高中家长协调沟通，这些家长也就是我们的客户，所以<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在这过程中我还需要学习一些媒体与市场的关系，以便更好地了解客户需求等，这就与 BU 的申请项目非常 match了。</span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span></span>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea99be7ae50ef62882ff933" style="width: 575px; height: 369px;"/></span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-size: 12px;">（运动 never stop！）</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="" style="margin: 0px 7px 11px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(20, 85, 87); border-top-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-right-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-left-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-radius: 3px; line-height: 36px; background: rgb(40, 167, 169);">往新领域尝试</span></strong></span>                </section>            </section>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">因为喜欢体育运动，尤其是篮球，所以在大三上学期，我通过<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在学校一个名叫“职为你来”的分享会上投递简历，拿到了凤凰网内容部体育频道新闻编辑的实习。</span>这段经历可以称得上是我大学四年中最累的一段日子了，那时我每天早上 8 点起床上课上到 12 点，然后吃了午饭就跑去凤凰网实习，从下午 3 点一直工作到晚上 10 点，而且时常碰到一些体育赛事结束得比较晚，往往 11 点才能下班，但那段日子也累并充实着，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">因为从之前的传统媒体跨到新媒体实习，接触到全新领域后我每天也像海绵一样不断吸收着。</span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">我当时的工作内容有<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">使用 CMCC （中国移动）后台、发布体育热点资讯、参与外勤活动直播等。</span>这个外勤活动其实是一个汽车频道负责的，因为我当时在体育频道表现比较好，他们那边的工作人员就把我挖过去协助做这样一个户外马拉松的活动。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea99c04ae50ef62882ff93a" style="width: 578px; height: 551px;"/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-size: 12px;">（在北二外的篮球场打球）</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">这段经历对我申请华盛顿大学的 Communication in Digital Media（数字媒体传播）和波士顿大学的 Emerging Media Studies（新兴媒体研究）帮助都非常大，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">因为这个活动形式是当下最新最火的视频直播，同时我还参与了品牌活动的前期策划等，这些都与 2 个学校的申请要求不谋而合，所以我就在文书重点强调了我是如何参与其中、整个流程是怎样的，以及我学到了些什么等等。</span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">其实在写文书之前我一直有一个误区，我认为应该重点突出自己未来的职业规划和情怀志向，而实习经历只需粗略的体现，但<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我的主导师 WW 姐点醒了我，告诉我写再多未来计划也是空话，</span>学校最感兴趣的是你曾经做过什么，对你有什么影响，你现在的状态怎样等。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">在准备文书的过程中我曾反复提出了 3 次不同的意见，但&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">WW 姐没有说一味地顺从我，而是明确告诉我想要申请美国的学校，我原本的思路是有问题的，一定要详细展现实习经历等，</span>所以最后我申请每个学校的文书都是结合实习经历来与之侧重匹配的，最后的申请结果也证明 WW 姐的坚持是非常正确的。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea99c24ae50ef62882ff942" style="width: 578px; height: 577px;"/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-size: 12px;">（与 WW 姐讨论文书，她纠正我的错误思路）</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="" style="margin: 0px 7px 11px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(20, 85, 87); border-top-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-right-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-left-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-radius: 3px; line-height: 36px; background: rgb(40, 167, 169);">宝贵的内推机会</span></strong></span>                </section>            </section>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">在大三下学期<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我作为系里的优秀学生被内推了一个中国国际广播电台（China Radio International）新媒体运营实习生的职位，</span>当时我们系里只有这一个名额，最后能得到这个机会我也觉得非常荣幸。因为这个平台是由之前的 4 家国家媒体合并在一起的，规格非常高，去到那边后也能感受到接触的资源都非常好，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">比如 Facebook 团队，或是路透社、法新社等外国媒体资源等。</span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">在这段实习期间，我主要负责新闻视频图文的编辑、做一些采访宣传、进行脸书直播互动等等，因为做事积极表现还不错，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我成功拿到了一位实习领导的推荐信，她是 CRI 的高级编辑与市场顾问，毕业于普渡大学，能在我的三封推荐信中有一封是出自美国大学毕业的老师这对我的申请来说大有裨益。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"></span><br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">总的来说我的三段实习是有一定逻辑关系的，第一段是在传统媒体第二段是在新媒体，第三段是在传统媒体的新媒体部，相当于<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">通过这 3 段实习我对传媒的各个领域都有所了解，</span>这种好的逻辑性和广的覆盖面都是在申请中学校非常看重的。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea99c48ae50ef62882ff947" style="width: 580px; height: 668px;"/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-size: 13.3333px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（在 CRI 的日子真的很宝贵~）</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="" style="margin: 0px 7px 11px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(20, 85, 87); border-top-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-right-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-left-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-radius: 3px; line-height: 36px; background: rgb(40, 167, 169);">申请这一路的成长</span></strong></span>                </section>            </section>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <section>                <section>                    <section></section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;"><strong>Match 太重要</strong></span>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">我一共申请了 11 个 program，最后拿到了 7 个 offer，对于这个结果我还是比较满意的，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">尤其是拿到了我最想去的哥大</span>。在一开始选校时我和 WW 姐就是<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">以城市作为方向来选择的</span>，毕竟像新闻传媒这样的专业，学校地理位置真的很关键。除了华盛顿大学，其他的选校名单基本都围绕在纽约、波士顿和洛杉矶，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">最后 WW 姐也按照难度划分给我合理规划了这些学校的层级排序。</span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">在文书上<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">主导师和专业导师教会我一个最大的点就是 match。</span></strong>她们会帮助我了解各个学校的具体要求和录取偏好，也会给我及时截官网的信息提醒我。比如申请的<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">南加大 Communication Management项目更偏商业化一点，我就会更着重凤凰网的经历，哥大偏教育我就着重第一段经历，</span>有的学校如果新媒体和传统媒体都有研究，那我就会强调第一段和第三段经历。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea99c7cae50ef62882ff94e" style="width: 582px; height: 1066px;"/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-size: 12px;">（WW 姐告诉我各个学校的专业设置与课程特点）</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">另外比如像<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">纽约大学 Media, Culture, and Communication 这个项目会比较注重学术文章和学生文采等，我就会稍微弱化实习经历，重点写我在校内的一些学术研究，</span>把我看过的名著观点作为引子来展开对跨文化研究的思考，促使我做相关的实习，提高个人能力和办事效率等。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">除此之外&nbsp;<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">WW 姐也会给我查一些学校的课，根据这些学校的课程内容，再在各个学校的文书中点出对这些课的看法，</span>从而把每封文书都显得更具针对性、内容更真实，这样呈现出来的质量也更高。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;">                <br/>            </p>            <section>                <section>                    <section></section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;"><strong>真情实感的推荐</strong></span>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">推荐信除了前面提到的普渡大学老师，另外 2 封我找的是课堂上与我互动最多的 2 位副教授，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在准备推荐信之前棕榈的导师也一直在跟我强调推荐人的职称不是很重要，</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">譬如学校领导的职称比较高，但是学生与校领导的接触往往没有与自己专业的授课老师多，如果校领导不是很了解你，或者你们没有什么共事的经历，写出的推荐信也不会很具有说服力。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">所以最后我找的是与我关系很好的 2 位副教授，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">因为平时我在他们的课上表现都比较积极，课下也会找他们讨论学术问题和期中期末作业等，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">再加上我参加过一些校园比赛和运动会，为学院赢得过一些荣誉，给他们留下了不错的印象，所以最后</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">他们为我写的推荐信都比较真情实感，说服力强。</span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span></span>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea99cd4ae50ef62882ff955" style="width: 590px; height: 373px;"/></span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（运动会冲刺时的抓拍，有点糊~）</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-size: 13.3333px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <section>                <section>                    <section></section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;"><strong>考语言别操之过急</strong></span>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">我的托福考了好几次，第一次考托福时因为不适应考题最后成绩不到 90，第二次好好准备后考到了 103。在这里我也想跟大家分享我的一个失败经验，我当时 6 月份第二次托福考到了103 后，因为想刷到 105 以上（毕竟在申请中 1 分的差距都能拉开许多人），我急于求成没到 1 个月又报名了一场，结果只考了102，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">事实证明间隔的时间太短没做好充分准备最终收效并不大，</span>所以我想告诉大家没准备好就不要着急去报名，不然最后花了钱和精力成绩没提升得不偿失。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea99cfcae50ef62882ff95a" style="width: 591px; height: 402px;"/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-size: 12px;">（想拿高分，多啃几本几百页厚书是必须的）</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="" style="margin: 0px 7px 11px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(20, 85, 87); border-top-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-right-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-left-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-radius: 3px; line-height: 36px; background: rgb(40, 167, 169);">不忘初心，方得始终</span></strong></span>                </section>            </section>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">我当初之所以想要出国就是<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">考虑到我的本科学校竞争力不强，所以为了以后能去到更好的就业平台，我想要进一步深造。</span>当然我也曾经在考研和出国二者之间纠结过，但因为我当时四六级的英语都达到了 600 多分，且考研只有一门英语，不像在出国中英语占的比重大，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">所以综合比较下来我觉得出国更加帮助我在英语上与别人拉开差距，更能发挥我的优势，也建议大家要擅用自己的长处去与别人竞争。</span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">确定出国目标后我就对找机构比较上心，最后签约棕榈有一个很大的原因是<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我当时有一个认识的同专业学姐也是在棕榈的帮助下去到了哥大，我觉得有这种活生生的案例在自己身边会比较有说服力。</span>另外一个比较直接的原因就是<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">棕榈的合同条款是我接触了多家机构后写得最明白最清楚的</span>，给人感觉最靠谱的，通过我现在的申请结果也证明我当初的决定没有错。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea99d1dae50ef62882ff960" style="width: 585px; height: 433px;"/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（最后送大家一个笑脸哈哈）</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(165, 170, 194); font-size: 13.3333px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">最后我想说准备出国的过程是很漫长的，我也有过一些难熬的时刻，每当这种时候我就想着<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">要对得起当初自己做的决定，要想着自己在未来拿到 offer 那一刻会多么有成就感。</span>行百里者半九十，越到后期阶段，越为关键越不能放弃。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">不忘初心，方得始终。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">希望学弟学妹们都能在未来斩获梦校 offer！<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"></span></span>            </p>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section>                                        <section>                                            <section>                                                <hr style="margin: 0px; padd