  <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <hr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"/>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <br/>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">学习最关键的两点</strong>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我和大部分同学可能不太一样，我很少去图书馆或者自习室，几乎都是在寝室学习，这主要源于<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我是一个很容易焦虑的人</span>，如果我处在一个大家都在拼命学的环境下，我会觉得压力很大学不进去，相反在寝室的话我会更加放松自在，效率也更高。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">想要在学习上取得好成绩我觉得关键在于 2 点，一是找到适合自己的模式，就像我喜欢在寝室学，而很多同学则偏向在图书馆、自习室学，或者喜欢在家学习等，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">总之找到对自己收效显著的那一种就行。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">第 2 点也是最重要的一点，那就是执行力。众所周知大学主要靠自觉，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">如果你能在大一大二比较早的时候就做到平时学，且每周定期做一个总结，那你至少可以为后面铺好很多路。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">因为通常刚进大学那 2 年大家的状态都比较松懈，如果你能把握住机会你就比较容易超越许多人。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea97a3fae50ef62882ff800" style="width: 563px; height: 391px;"/></span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我觉得我自己算是一个比较自律的人吧，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">之所以能在寝室学的进去也是因为我这个人挺无聊的，没什么兴趣爱好，也不会特别沉迷一些休闲娱乐等，就算偶尔有我也能很快抽离出来。</span>所以一般在寝室的话我是空闲了就去学，没有规定要学几个小时，因为一旦给自己施压我的心理情况就不是很好，也学不进去，所以放松自然的状态最适合我。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">至关重要的切身影响</strong>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">如果给我的自律程度打分，我想可能是中等水平以上，但要是和我的专业导师相比的话，我这些根本不算什么。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我的专业导师本科是普通 211，最后申到了哈佛耶鲁、宾大哥大、布朗杜克等 13 所名校，</span>他是一个追求完美，对自己要求很高的人。在接受他辅导的过程中，能感受到他非常精益求精，不管是专业知识还是学习规划我都从他那里学到了很多，同时<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">他的这种精神也激励着我，让我知道我应该去成为一个更加自律的人，</span>能在申请路上遇到他我觉得自己真的非常幸运。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea97a6bae50ef62882ff805" style="width: 567px; height: 383px;"/></span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">首先我的专业导师<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在信息搜集整理方面非常擅长，因为他现在正在哈佛就读生统这个专业，所以他认识很多生统不同方向的人，能够接触到最前沿最热门的相关项目方向，</span>这些对于我这个转专业的初级者了解生统从而更好地去选校帮助是非常大的。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">比如在一开始对于各个学校的生统项目，我只有一个大概的了解，一些具体的课程设置和录取偏好我完全不清楚，专业导师就为我补充提供了很多这方面的信息，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">像有一些学校对转专业的同学是更友好的，知道这样的信息对于我这个很容易焦虑的人来说也能增强一些自信，心态也会更好。</span></span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">不过现在回看选校申请，我还是有一些遗憾的，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">因为我自己一直不自信很焦虑，老是怕没学校录取，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">所以在棕榈按照梯度帮我申了 7 所学校后，我自己又去申了好几所保底校，浪费了很多钱，如果能重来的话，我可能会选择冲击一下更好的学校，这也是我想给大家分享的一个经验教训。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea97a8aae50ef62882ff809" style="width: 567px; height: 388px;"/></span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">其次最重要的一点是我的专业导师<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在生统专业各种申请材料的准备上非常有经验有策略，</span>在准备文书的时候，他给我看了他自己当时申请时写的 personal statement，一方面看到他那些令人惊叹的各种经历我会备受激励，另一方面<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">他用他自身的案例向我展示如何把众多看起来不太相关的经历用一个清楚的主题串联起来，同时也教会我有一些比较小的事情可以通过包装充实它，</span>挖掘一些闪光的部分，从而有机会成为招生官眼中的亮点。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">在上文书课的时候，他先看了一下我有什么经历，然后教我如何把这些零碎的事情找到一个主线串联起来建立逻辑。当时他给我想的是<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">开篇先突出我在成绩这方面的优势，写一下课程方面的优异表现等，紧接着阐述与生统相关的一些科研经历，最后展示暑期项目社团活动等。</span>在这个梳理经历的过程中也可以逐步回答文书提出的几点要求（如为什么对生统感兴趣、为什么选这个学校这个项目等）。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea97a9eae50ef62882ff810" style="width: 569px; height: 377px;"/></span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">不得不说专业导师上的这个文书课真的非常到位，当时他给我从头到尾缕了一遍之后，我瞬间就知道应该怎么来写了，效果非常明显，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我清楚记得当时是在十一假期我花了 3 天就完成了初稿</span>，虽然后面反复打磨了很多次，但一开始简历的整体逻辑是没什么变动的，这个过程能这么顺利离不开他这一路的指导。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">最后<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我的专业导师还是一个非常清楚自己目标的人</span>，各个阶段他都知道自己想要什么，然后朝着目标前进，不会做什么无谓的事情。比如他之前跟我讲他考托福的故事，他考到 109 后，他还想再去刷一下，其实当时他其他各方面的背景条件都非常出色了，这个 109 的成绩也不差，但为了冲刺更高等级的学校，他又把成绩刷到了 114，虽然看起来只提高了 5 分，但是要付出的努力也是非常多的，而这 5 分在申请中能够甩开很多人，所以最后他能以一个普通 211 的本科申到这么多顶尖名校我由衷的佩服他。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">他在选择上目的明确，不会纠结迷茫的这种务实品质恰恰是我本人非常欠缺的</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">，因为我之前就因为纠结保研还是出国浪费了很多时间和机会，所以<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">和他相处的过程也是一个不断挖掘自身、反省自己的过程，我也非常享受这个一直学习汲取的过程。</span></span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span></span>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea97ab9ae50ef62882ff814" style="width: 556px; height: 395px;"/></span></span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">不可或缺的辅导鼓励</strong>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">如果说专业导师是我申请上的规划师和领航员，那<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">主导师应该就是我的倾听者和加油站</span>了，从网申开始，一直到拿 offer 前的两三个月，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我因为太焦虑，整个人是处在一个风声鹤唳、草木皆兵的状态之中的，</span>那段时间我只要一看到什么关于申请局势的推送（比如说什么中美关系形式严峻，或 2019 年有可能成为申请美国最难的一年等类似文章），<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我就会特别紧张心急，担心没学校录取，失学什么的，然后我就会立马去找我的主导师问她该怎么办，</span>她也总是会鼓励我让我更自信一点并且为我提供帮助等。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">因为我本身并不是一个乐观豁达的人，会很容易陷入焦虑的情绪，所以从我的角度来说我其实并不太希望我的导师是一个非常温柔，与我自身人设太相似的人，因为这样的话我觉得可能合作起来效率不是很高，但<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我的主导师与我是完全相反的，她是一个典型的北方女孩儿，特别开朗活泼，说话也很有趣，这就与我非常互补。</span></span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span></span>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea97aeeae50ef62882ff81a" style="width: 559px; height: 400px;"/></span></span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">同时她也是一个执行力很强的人，很会安排组织事情，监督我各个阶段应该做什么。我记得当时在申请之前因为本专业的数理相关课程比较少，对于申请生统来说只能达到一个最基本的门槛，所以为了更有把握<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">主导师就让我尽量在学校多选一些相关课程，她说如果学校能选就尽量在学校选，如果不能选就去 coursera 上选一些网课，</span>最后我就在学校选了一门，在 coursera 上选了一些，提前打下申请所需的这部分基础。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">当然在申请过程中主导师的付出也是非常多的，比如选校时她为我整理了 10 几个学校的备选，把这些学校的信息全部整理到一个 Excel 表格里，然后从中来筛选，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">这种信息的整合对于申请来说是非常省事、有用的。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">文书打磨的过程她也很负责，当时<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">她指出我的文书在言辞上过于感性浪漫，不够实用理性，</span>可能有一些招生委员看起来就像散文一样，不如像看说明文或者议论文那样更突出自身特色，所以<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">她就在征求我的意见的基础上加入了一些我欠缺的东西，</span>让整个文书看起来更加饱满完整。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea97b0dae50ef62882ff821" style="width: 565px; height: 412px;"/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">确定目标尽快行动</strong>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我之所以会在申请季如此的焦虑，是因为我决定出国的时间特别仓促，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我其实大一就想好要出国的，但大三我又动摇想保研了，大三上的时候我觉得先保研试一试，但最终大三下结束时我又决定还是要出国，一是我不太喜欢本专业想转专业到生统，二是想去美国感受一下更先进的教育，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">所以其实大三那一段黄金时间，我是完全耽误了的，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">因为对于保研和出国应该怎么来安排是完全不同的。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">对于保研来说主要是看成绩和排名，所以大三那一年我的所有重点都放在 GPA 上，一直专注在上课考试上面，但如果是出国的话，GPA 只是其中一个指标，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我可以利用这段时间去找暑研，或是出去交流交换等，但因为那时想保研我丧失了这些很好的时机，这也是我一直很后悔的地方，</span>毕竟如果有海外经历的话对于申请来说是非常加分的，说不定我还可以去冲刺更高 level 的学校。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea97b30ae50ef62882ff828" style="width: 577px; height: 371px;"/></span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">同时</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">那时我还没有 GRE 和托福成绩</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">，只有雅思，当时会有雅思成绩是因为在大一时想出国，但对考语言没什么概念，听别人说考雅思之后申英美都可以用我就去考了。虽然导师之后告诉我雅思同样可以申，但看到身边的同学大部分都考了托福，且雅思考了 2 次后都没法刷到更高的分（普遍来说雅思刷分是比托福更难的），我<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">就还是想咬咬牙在大四刚开学再去考一次托福，同时我要考 GRE，所以那段时间就把自己搞的很忙碌很慌张。</span></span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">处在申请的当下，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我那种因为后悔而痛苦焦虑的情绪就愈加明显，</span>就时常会去想为什么之前要纠结那么久，不坚定出国的决心，尤其是看到身边的同学都在准备申请材料了我还在考托福和 GRE 就会更加后悔之前为什么浪费了那么多时间，如果能早一点确定目标，也能更加针对性的去准备。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">所以我也想用我自己的经历告诉大家如果能<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">早点看清楚自己想要干什么，不要犹豫，尽快行动起来，</span>同时在申请中要保持一颗平常心，就算偶尔有压力，但也不要让自己过度紧张，在很多事情已经成为既定事实之后就不要再去纠结多想，而是要专注做好当下。</span>        </p>    </section>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section>                                        <hr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"/>                                        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                            <br/>                                        </p>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: 