r: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                        <br/>                                    </p>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">今年 4 月，距离提交申请已经过去了 116 天，我在位于美国纽约市北部的 Colgate University 收到了来自梦校哥大的 offer ，我和嘉怡导师都松了一口气。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我自认为我不是理工科背景特别强的申请者，从来就不是。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我本科的大学是 Carnegie Mellon University ，但是我所在的商学院人才济济，上了一个学期之后，我发现身边的同学都太厉害了，他们的数学、 CS 都学得特别好，跟不上他们是一种很无力、很糟糕的感觉。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在巨大的压力之下，我只能思考如何在能力范围之内把成绩提升上去，也许需要改变策略。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">回溯最初，我是想先打好数学基础，再学习金融的，但在 CMU 转专业很困难，所以不如按照最初的规划，找个地方先把数学学好。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">于是上完第一个学期，我就转学到了 Colgate University 文理学院。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">现在来看，文理学院的环境更加地适合我，我从一个轻易就会被“淹没”的环境逃到了岸边，得以喘息，遇见了春暖花开。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea9724bae50ef62882ff792" style="width: 649px; height: 427px;"/></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;">（图片由学员提供，未经允许不得转载）</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">因为一位教授的原因，大二的时候，学校增开了一门完全对我胃口的应用数学学科，我们成为了这个分支的第一批学生。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">小班形式授课的文理学院有一个很照顾学生的优点，就是教授和学生的距离很近，课程的质量也很高，像私人定制的感觉，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">老师会知道我需要上哪些课程，也会单独为我做一些对申请和未来道路有帮助的建议。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我在这样的环境中收获了更加清晰的人生规划，在数理学科中比较如鱼得水，和教授们的关系也处得非常好。</span><br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">但是并不是所有的事情都那么完美。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">文理学院对理科专业的学生同样开设了社会科学和人文课程，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">但我是一名典型的偏科生，我知道数学、计算机、经济等相关会对未来起关键作用，就学得很用功，几乎是全 A 的分数；</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">文科的分数，就佛系看待了。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">这也直接影响了我的 GPA ，这是后话。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea9726bae50ef62882ff798" style="width: 646px; height: 437px;"/></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;">（图片由学员提供<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">，未经允许不得转载</span>）</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; margin-block-start: 1em; margin-block-end: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">我在登山中看懂了投资</strong></span>                                </p>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">相比于佛系，狂野可能更能形容另一个我。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我热衷于登山、滑雪、骑行等等户外运动。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我爬的第一座雪山是四姑娘山的第三座山峰，那是我第一次爬海拔超过 5 千米的雪山。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">前面都挺顺利，就在即将迎接胜利的的时候，这个故事迎来了遗憾。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">冲顶前的那个夜晚，我因为高原反应几乎一夜没睡，而连下了一夜的大雪也让前路变得困难而危险，冲顶的胜利好像在向着不可能方向靠近。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">天亮起来的时候，考虑了很久很久的我做出了放弃冲顶的决定。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">这对我来说是一个不小的遗憾，却也令我看懂了很多关于投资的问题，虽然这两者看起来并没有什么关联。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">除了运动之外，我最大的爱好就是每天都花时间管理自己的账户，通过自己控制仓位、自己选择股票来找经济周期和市场规律，先保证不亏本再思考怎么跟上行情，最好还能够稍微赚点小钱。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea97288ae50ef62882ff7a0" style="width: 650px; height: 401px;"/></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(178, 178, 178);">（管理个人账户，今年的收益曲线）</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我觉得登山和投资很像，在明知道会有潜在风险的时候，你是选择不顾一切地去冒险，还是及时止损和进行风险控制？</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">很多事情都是在一念之间。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">在我自己做美股账户的时候，我觉得投资市场就像大自然，人在自然面前是很渺小的，其实作为一个投资者、交易者，在市场中也是很渺小的一份子，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">你并不能战胜市场，你只能尽可能去研究它，让自己去适应市场，看能不能在市场中取得一定的成功。</span><br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">后来的我也在不断地挑战自我，甚至登上了海拔 6 千米的雪峰，但是我依然敬畏自然，在惊叹大自然的伟大和神奇当中感受愿望达成的满足，就像在市场的汹涌波涛中激荡沉浮享受乐趣。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea972b3ae50ef62882ff7a3" style="width: 642px; height: 430px;"/></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;">（图片由学员提供<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">，未经允许不得转载</span>）</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; margin-block-start: 1em; margin-block-end: 1em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">只有藤校能满足我的“藤校情结”</strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 30px;"></span>                                </p>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">能把喜爱好和擅长结合起来的事情，除了登山，还有金融数学。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section>                                        <strong style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">选专业</strong><br/>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">因为我本身是数学专业，以后打算从事金融方面的工作，所以我想在专业领域里面钻研得更深一点，金融数学专业会比较适合我。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">对于和我一样读研不读博的同学来说，研究生阶段的专业基本是为了就业去考虑的，所以</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在专业选择上，我的建议会是先对自我准确定位，选择一个适合个人兴趣和未来发展的专业，这可能会影响你的就读体验和人生路线。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section>                                        <strong style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">选学校</strong><br/>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我在四年前申美本的时候就知道进常春藤可能非常难。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">四年下来，上藤校的名校情结一直没变，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">选定了金融数学之后，衡量了自身条件，我觉得冲一冲也许申哥大会有戏，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">于是把哥大定成了我的冲刺校。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我在大三才下定决心读研，大四才开始找机构，属于名副其实的“晚申党”，在光鲜亮丽的哥大 offer 背后，我也经历了差点没学上的煎熬。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea972f0ae50ef62882ff7aa" style="width: 645px; height: 481px;"/></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">（图片由学员提供<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">，未经允许不得转载</span>）</span></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section>                                        <strong style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">选机构</strong><br/>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">迫于课业的压力和时间的步步紧逼，我决定寻求机构的帮助。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我开始在网上搜索靠谱的申请机构，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">看了一些案例之后，再结合用户的好评度，选机构这件事情有了结果。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我在 2018 年 10 月和棕榈大道签约了，选择了<a href="http://undefined" target="_blank" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: var(--weui-LINK); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); cursor: pointer; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">“一所全程”</a>的服务，之后的每一步，我都离哥大越走越近。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section>                                        <strong style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">GPA不高、实习没亮点怎么办？</strong><br/>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">相比于其他申请金融数学的学霸来说，我这个偏科生实在不占优势， GPA 3.54 是我的软肋。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">因为本科的学校比较小，很多数学课一年只有一次机会上，大四下学期才有高难度的统计课等重要的课程，所以申请时提交的成绩单里就没办法包含这些课的成绩，而相应地招生官自然也无法看到这些。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">申请季的时候，我正在上大四上学期的概率课，我和嘉怡老师讨论对策，结论是我必须拿到概率课A的成绩，才会对我的申请起到帮助。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">事实证明确实如此，我在这门课上下了苦功夫，有一丁点不明白的就去找老师弄明白，最后如愿拿到 A 。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">提交申请的时候，我的 GPA 成绩提到了 3.6 ，刚刚够得上指标，更重要的是，这一张成绩单上，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">与数理相关的专业课程我都拿了 A ，让学校认为我是有能力学好所申请的专业的。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">所以我用切身体会换来的经验就是：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">尽可能当“早起鸟”，决定好你要申请的专业，然后去研究那些项目看重的课程，提前把节奏安排好。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea974baae50ef62882ff7bf" style="width: 653px; height: 490px;"/></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(178, 178, 178);">（图片由学员提供<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">，未经允许不得转载</span>）</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我的实习经历也没有特别的亮眼，但是招生官会很重视这一块。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">专业导师在指导写文书上的时候和我的想法一致，就是</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">将所有的经历都往金融量化上面去体现，突出表现能力方面，从我有的实习中把他们想看到的一些特质尽可能地展现出来。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">比如我在管理自己的账户，在学校参加投资小组的经历，实习经历中关于资产管理、行业研究和二级市场等方面研究，我把细节尽可能写突出，体现出我做了很细致的的工作，表达一些关于实习项目的想法、反思和以后可以进步优化的点。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">通过这些方面的罗列和过程分析，招生官能够清楚地了解到我对专业的热衷程度和完成项目的能力。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">在文书的修改上，专业导师对专业词汇严谨性的把握令我叹服，也给出很多实用的修改意见。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">除了哥大之外，我还 DIY 申请了几所学校，以哥大的文书为基础，专业导师还额外帮我在文书上针对不同学校的做了个性化修改，让我这个晚申党在最早的 DDL 之前完成了全部的申请材料准备。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">对于缺少大牛实习的晚申党来说，文书里关于这方面的内容真的很重要，提一点小建议：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">文书要体现自己和项目契合的点，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">一个是大学课程与项目契合的地方，另一个是实习中和项目契合的地方，各挑一个重点详细去写，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">最好都要体现出你对这个专业的热爱，或者对这个职业目标的执着。</span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <br/>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea974e2ae50ef62882ff7c4" style="width: 648px; height: 449px;"/>                </p>                <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <br/>                </p>            </section>        </section>        <se