感兴趣。相比以理论为主的人文社科</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">，计算机基于理论但更重于实践，学成后自己就拥有一项实实在在的技术，未来就业也不容易吃亏。而且计算机专业不同于那些需要下工地的专业，基本不存在体力活</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">。所以我个人觉得女生就读计算机专业没有什么劣势。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">哥大这次在我们学校应该是录取了 3 个学生，我和同班的一个女生就占了两个名额（她虽然选校和我不太一样，但我们都收到了哥大 offer ，最后决定一起去哥大）！</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">所以不要小视&nbsp;Girls Power&nbsp;哈哈~&nbsp;</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea96f29ae50ef62882ff764" style="width: 635px; height: 397px;"/></span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;">想要申上哥大这种级别的藤校，优秀的 GPA&nbsp;是一个很好的加分项，但其实在大一时我也有过一段“小小放飞自我”的时光：报名参加了学校的民族舞社团。那时为了学校的演出，每天下课后大约有 4&nbsp;个小时的练习时间，自己的成绩也有所落下。但之后我奋起直追，拿下三次校级奖学金（一次一等奖）并参与了多段科研，</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">其中的一段大创项目经历让我接触到了许多&nbsp;Machine Learning 方向的知识，当时觉得特别有趣，而且它也是当下 CS 的大热门方向，那时我便决定在硕士阶段要朝这个方向继续深造!</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <br/>        </p>    </section>    <section>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            &nbsp;        </p>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section>                         