, 89); font-size: 14px;">大一的时候我听了一场麻省理工学姐的讲座，惊叹于她的能力，我也想成为那样酷的人，一个敢于追求并且愿意付诸行动的人。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">我非常喜欢会计，萌生了跨专业读研究生的想法，但当时我的老师觉得我的想法不切实际，因为我被寄托本专业保研的希望。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">后来深受乔布斯的鼓舞，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">“the only thing that kept me going was that I love what I did”，我下定决心往喜欢的会计方向发展事业。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">我开始早早准备，考各种会计证书、进行会计相关实习、发表相关论文。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">大四的时候我拿到本专业保研名额，但我决定放弃。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">当时我身边也有同学想要跨专业，最后却妥协了，可能是因为他们内心不够坚定且没有坚持付出。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">所以，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">当你选择将来要从事的领域，一定要找到你的激情所在，并做好为之奋斗的准备。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea96bacae50ef62882ff720" style="width: 668px; height: 333px;"/></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0px;">（乔布斯演讲中的一段话，我深受启发）</span><br/>            </p>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(178, 178, 178);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section></section>                                    <section>                                        <p>                                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">一段意义非凡的活动经历</span></strong>                                        </p>                                        <p>                                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><br/></span></strong>                                        </p>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">大一参加了学生会，但发现不太适合我，活动对我的吸引力不是很大，所以之后我就退出了。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">在大二期间，我和校内的国际志愿者一起举办了关于女性力量的女权主义活动，成立了校园女性组织，以此来帮助女性独立。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">这个活动得到了校园甚至 peace corps 的关注，为现代女性发声是我认为非常有意义的事情。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea96bc2ae50ef62882ff723" style="width: 606px; height: 458px;"/></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section></section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(178, 178, 178);">（受邀参加 peace corps 的 workshop）</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"></span><br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(178, 178, 178);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section></section>                                    <section>                                        <p>                                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">梦校 Baruch</span></strong>                                        </p>                                        <p>                                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><br/></span></strong>                                        </p>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">我通过自主组织的校园女权活动认识了几个国外的志愿者朋友，当听说我非常向往纽约时，她们提到&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">Baruch 是一个在纽约有 high reputation 的学校，毗邻华尔街，高就业率，课程设置符合 AICPA 的要求，并且学费相对低，性比价可以说非常高。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">对我来说，它可能是我发展会计事业最理想的跳板了。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">但是我咨询过一些学姐学长及导师之后，大家都认为 Baruch 是一个对 technical 要求很高的学校，里面的学生好多都是非常有经验的人士，这让我感到压力，同时能和这么多很酷的人一起学习又让我更加向往。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">于是，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">为了弥补我在 work experience 的缺陷，在准备 GT 的同时我开始长期实习，决定一心朝着 Baruch 努力。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">即使最后申 5 中 4 ，其它学校有更高的排名，但由于低成本留美的目标，我还是毅然选择 Baruch 。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea96bd9ae50ef62882ff728" style="width: 669px; height: 257px;"/></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section></section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(178, 178, 178);">（要靠誓必实现的决心认真地活着——山本耀司）</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"></span><br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(178, 178, 178);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section></section>                                    <section>                                        <section>                                            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在高压实习中飞速进步</strong></span>                                        </section>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">大二的时候我去香港宏利金融集团实习了一个月，作为 team leader 最后拿到了 return offer 。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">这段实习是对自己迅速适应的能力一个很好的锻炼，和来自不同学校的同学一起做 team work ，短时间掌握一个全新领域的专业知识以及对真实客户做 portfolio 。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">这一高压快节奏的工作让我对金融行业有了全新的认识。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">写文书的过程中，我的棕榈专业导师嘉怡老师帮我挖掘出这段经历的亮点，这段实习虽然不是在会计领域，但是这个经历体现着我的团队协作、数学计算、领导等能力，这也成了我文书比较核心的素材。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea96beeae50ef62882ff72c" style="width: 561px; height: 398px;"/></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section></section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;">（下班后的维多利亚港更加令人心动）</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"></span><br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">另一段实习是在大三，我在一家税务师事务所工作。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">刚开始，我只是做一些很基础的工作，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">但是当我发现事务所准备与一家投行公司组成团队去做项目时，我大胆毛遂自荐，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">想要获得成为团队一员的机会，结果也如愿以偿了。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">项目内事务繁杂，我完成分内工作后，经常主动帮助经理处理一些事情，也学习到很多干货，实习结束后，经理很乐意帮我写推荐信，到现在我们都维持着这段见证着我成长的友谊。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">所以，我认为主动争取提升自我的机会很重要；</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在实践中思考也是必要的。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">我在这段实习结束后更深刻的感触是在处理现实问题时，会计不是一个独立的个体，它与其他行业如金融、法律存在相互交织的联系，所以在之后的职业规划中我会更加关注到会计的综合发展方面。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea96c0aae50ef62882ff732" style="width: 566px; height: 513px;"/></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section></section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px;">（记录通宵加班后的一个早晨）</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"></span><br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section></section>                                    <section>                                        <section>                                            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">最低成本拿下语言考试</strong></span>                                        </section>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">关于 GT ，看到身边很多报了昂贵补习班但依旧考不出理想成绩的同学，我决定选择最低成本原则——自学，这是一个对自主性较高的同学最有效省钱的办法。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">托福我复习了两个月飘过 100 ，因为我不想花太多时间在这上面，所以只考了这一次。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">我认为</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">托福是一个可以提高自身英语综合能力的考试，不断练习，认真备考就会有质的提升，越早考出来它会成为自身的一个优势，比如找实习。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">关于 GMAT ，第一次因为轻敌不够坚定而惨败，自信心受到重挫，同时又是我独自在外地实习的期间，孤独又无助，还好嘉怡老师在这期间不断鼓励我、督促我，要我重新找自己的错误，冷静分析好好准备，最后赶在规划时间考出了成绩。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">有一个小 tip ，我发现考完 GMAT 再去看托福阅读真的很简单，因为 GMAT 对逻辑以及阅读速度的训练非常到位，如果规划时间很紧，不如先考 GMAT ，这样不用花太多时间准备托福。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea96c2fae50ef62882ff73f" style="width: 579px; height: 615px;"/></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0px;">（孤独的备考路上这只小可爱陪伴着我）</span><br/>            </p>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section></section>                                    <section>                                        <section>                                            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">文书修改精益求精</strong></span>                                        </section>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">由于我准备申请时正在实习的忙乱时期，自己的精力没有办法让我充足准备应对申请季的慌乱，想要有人指导同时也想自己掌握主动权。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">找了几家中介，短短几句话就能让我感觉到他们居高临下的态度，这令我很头疼。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">直到遇见棕榈，我毫不犹豫选择了棕榈的半 DIY 辅导。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">我觉得</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">半 DIY 性价比很高，而且这个流程非常有特色，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">一个 team 包括主导师+专业导师+外教，简历、文书等都是先上课、讨论、挖掘素材，再开始写作以及进行无数次修改。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在申请 Baruch 的其中一篇文书写作中，嘉怡老师帮我挖掘亮点，阐述了我想为社会女性做出贡献的想法并付诸了一定的行动，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">以及未来想为职场女性做出更多改变。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">这使得我的文书优势比较突出，作为新一代独立女性，我证明了自己的独立思想。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">学校想要的不仅是优秀的学术人才，更是有社会责任感的新力量。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">感谢在这期间嘉怡老师每次都和我一起耐心修改，文书修改了不下 20 次，直到大家都满意。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">看到嘉怡老师在申请季常常为了帮同学赶 DDL 熬夜，觉得她真的很负责。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">最后选校的时候她也是鼓励我遵从自己的内心，真的是是亦师亦友的存在。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">还有我的专业导师 dancy ，她毕业于 Baruch 的会计专业，期间提供给我很多 insight 的意见，包括学校喜欢什么样的学生、看重哪些品质等。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;">在文书写作过程给了很大的帮助，在有限的字数里教我如何更好地用自己的经历来体现能力。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: