          content: '<h2 class="rich_media_title" id="activity-name" style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal;">    北大降分录取、考神级别也被网申吓懵，他是如何拿下伯克利哥大 offer 的？</h2><p>    <br/></p><p>    <br/></p><div class="rich_media_content " id="js_content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; position: relative; z-index: 0; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; visibility: visible;">    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">同学在刷夜备考的时候，他在休息放松；同学看每个知识点都像考题的时候，他轻易就 get 到了考点，在这么优秀的学霸眼里，估计所有的困难都会自动降低等级吧？</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">其实不！他说：“在网申、简历、文书面前，我直接懵逼了！” 🤯</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">棕榈学员&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">Scott</strong></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></strong></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea95b83ae50ef62882ff645" style="width: 419px; height: 286px;"/></strong></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></strong></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: left; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <strong style="text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 0px;">&nbsp;本科：</span></strong><span style="text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">北京大学</span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: left; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <strong style="text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;GPA：</span></strong><span style="text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">3.84/4.00 (3/207)</span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: left; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <strong style="text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;GRE：</span></strong><span style="text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">333</span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: left; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <strong style="text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;TOEFL：</span></strong><span style="text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">107</span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: left; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <strong style="text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;Offer：&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">哥伦比亚大学 商业分析</span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">加州大学伯克利分校 电子和计算机工程</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">加州大学戴维斯分校 商业分析</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">Final Decision：</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">加州大学伯克利分校</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section></section>                    <section></section>                    <section></section>                </section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(40, 167, 169); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">跳过高考，直录北大CS</strong></strong></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">从高中开始，我就一直在学物理奥赛，获得过省赛一等奖，也</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">因为参加北大物理夏令营被北大降一本线录取，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">成为工学院的新生。因为对 CS 的热爱，我大二转系到了信息科学技术学院，大三通过成绩和面试被选拔到拔尖班。说起我选择 CS 专业，除了热爱，另外一个原因</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">是我父亲的鼓励。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我的父亲在一个传统工业公司工作，当时公司正在往工业 4.0 人工智能方向转型，他看到了计算机这个行业在未来的巨大潜力，但是人才也在更新换代，在这个浪潮中他觉得自己的发展空间没有那么大了，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">他将希望寄托在我的身上，希望我能抓住机会，在计算机领域有一番作为。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在我看来，计算机是一个基础工具，熟练掌握它之后我的发展面会更广，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">所以从大学起，我的目标就是将掌握的计算机技能应用到日常生活中去。所以在大学的头两年，我将重点放在学好理论、打好基础、拿好成绩上，为读研的铺一条踏实的道路。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea95bbaae50ef62882ff64b"/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section></section>                    <section></section>                    <section></section>                </section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(40, 167, 169); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">拿好成绩其实是有诀窍的</strong></strong></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">没有人不想拿到好成绩，但是毕竟天才少之又少，我刚好不是其中的一个，所以我针对自己总结了一套能拿好成绩的方法。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">在别人眼里，我是一个很擅长考试的人，可能也是其他家长口中“别人家的孩子”。虽然每个人的学习方法都不一样，但是</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我在考前的轻松休闲跟别人比起来还是显得有些格格不入，我几乎没有熬夜、刷夜准备考试的经历，我是把功夫更多地下在平时，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">所以考前稍微复习一下就可以了，其他时间就打打球什么的放松放松。其实应对考试这件事情，是有诀窍的。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea95bedae50ef62882ff64e" style="width: 525px; height: 674px;"/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178); letter-spacing: 0.544px;">（图片由学员提供，未经允许不得转载）</span><br/>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我首先会思考哪些点可能会考到，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">从经历过的大大小小的考试来看，出题老师不会纠结于太多的细节题。我们学习的知识大致上可以分为两类，有的是需要掌握技能的，有的是网上或者手边的资料可以查到的，可以查到的东西一般就不会考。所以很多同学会在期末考试之前在群里为一个旁支末节的知识点讨论半天，在我看来有些本末倒置了，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">出题人其实更看重的是如何在考卷中体现你的学习能力，而不是记忆力。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">第 2 点就是，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在拿到题的时候，我会揣测出题人的想法，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">比如他希望我能够回答什么内容，所以我要站在他的角度来思考，往他希望那个方向去回答，而不是站在自己的角度瞎答。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">而在平时，有不懂的我也随时</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">跟老师交流，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">因为我觉得我不懂的老师肯定懂，他讲了我就明白了，而且跟老师交流会给他留一个好的印象，他会觉得这个学生学习态度很好。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea95c4cae50ef62882ff65a"/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section></section>                    <section></section>                    <section></section>                </section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(40, 167, 169); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">GRE 很难，但我有蒙答案的办法</strong></strong></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我一直都有出国的想法，本科的前两年，我主攻 GPA ，大三开始做科研、考 GRE 、暑研、实习、考托福。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我现在依然觉得 GRE 挺难的，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">当时我在单词题和阅读题都遇到了不小的麻烦。GRE 不像专业考试那么好找诀窍，很多都靠记忆、积累和语感，一开始做题还挺挫败的。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">所以我非常同意 GRE 早考早完事的说法，而且考过了 GRE ，考托福的时候也会更得心应手。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我当时做阅读的时候经常做不完，做题的时候非常焦虑，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">感觉时间很赶，读不进去，做题的时候就很勉强，对时间不够的那种恐惧占据了阅读的整个过程，所以效果极差，而且一直无法克服这个问题。在离考试还有两三个星期的关键时期，我决定放下卷子，和父母出国走走。很难得地有这么一个机会换个心境，放空大脑，去享受旅途，回来之后心态就调整过来了，做题变得很高效。所以，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">适当地停下来，比一直钻牛角尖要有用得多；</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">而且做阅读题的时候有一个小技巧，就是</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">不要总暗示自己做不完题目，专注在段落里面，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">主动地去汲取阅读中的一些知识，去思考，读这句话之后接下来可能会说什么，专注度和准确率都会提高很多。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea95c6aae50ef62882ff65c" style="width: 598px; height: 349px;"/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178);">（旅途中，德国新天鹅堡）</span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">在做单词题的时候我主要靠蒙，是不是很荒谬？其实是我学了一种构词法，就是</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">通过词根词缀去猜意思，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">因为很多时候并不是非要你知道这个单词的准确意思，更多的是知道</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">它是一个正相似还是一个负相似，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">所以词根词缀就是我蒙答案的关键。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section></section>                    <section></section>                    <section></section>                </section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(40, 167, 169); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">对不起，对申请这件事我真是两眼一抹黑</strong></strong></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">当时我就觉得，大多数人都是第一次申请，别人都知道怎么操作，为什么就我觉得这么难？</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">去年夏天，我母亲在别的家长的好评中认识了棕榈，让我和前期咨询老师聊一聊，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">聊完之后我觉得棕榈实事求是、不自吹自擂的态度特别靠谱和踏实，就合作了。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">对于申请的诸多未知事宜，也得到了解答。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">因为我申请加入了棕榈的</span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">合伙人计划（好像又叫先锋玩家），</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">后来棕榈不仅帮我配备了最顶级的&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">“主导师+专业导师+班主任+外教”&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">辅导团队，专业导师雪峰老师是哈佛的 CS 专业毕业，外教是伯克利、斯坦福毕业，辅导团队非常的专业，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">后来还免费帮我做了选校、文书、简历、推荐信等辅导，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">感觉自己特别幸运，不仅能遇到这么</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">优秀的导师，还节省了很大一笔申请费用。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">所以大家如果感兴趣的话也可以咨询下看看今年还有没有这个计划。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea95c98ae50ef62882ff662" style="width: 603px; height: 403px;"/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178); letter-spacing: 0.544px;">（图片由学员提供，未经允许不得转载）</span></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">选校，我连官网都看不懂。</strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">一开始我对学校什么的完全不了解，我看</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">每个学校的官网都长得不一样，找起信息来非常麻烦，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">然后也 get 不到最重要的点，更不知道什么学校该选什么学校不该选。这个时候我的主导师 Olive 老师和雪峰老师就比较操心，雪峰老师对于 CS 这个领域的各个项目的优劣势都比较清楚，这也省去了我很多了解的过程，因为</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">这些信息在网上是搜集不到的，所有的学校都只显示优势，需要跟专业的人聊才能对比出这个学校的优劣势，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">所以从雪峰老师那里，我了解到很多的学校和项目的信息。</span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">针对我的情况，老师们推荐了很多学校作为备选，也教给了我许多技巧，包括拉开梯度，有一些保底、有一些冲刺。我根据这份选校名单再有针对地去查每个项目，去官网看课程设置和培养方向，在这之间选一些我比较中意的项目。这样一来节省了很多的时间，也使得选校的思路变得非常清晰有条理。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">在选校的时候我也会经常纠结，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">这个学校到底是选还是不选，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">老师教了一个比较好的方法，我推荐给学弟学妹：</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">假设，你除了这个项目，其他所有的项目都被拒了，你去不去？</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">要是觉得算了我明年再申，或者我就不出国了，那就别申，要是觉得就算只有这个项目录了我也会去，那就一定要申。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea95ccaae50ef62882ff66a"/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">选校的难题解决了之后，网申的时候我又遇到了难题。</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我还是在一堆长得不一样的官网中不知所措，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我不知道具体每一块怎么填，因为有挺多细节的东西，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">万一哪个选项选错了，会有什么后果我也不知道，于是我向老师们求助，我的班主任对网申系统十分熟悉，在通话中，她以其中一个网申系统做例子，我们细致地过了一遍，搞清楚了所有的点。之后我遇到什么问题会在群里提问，老师们也会非常详细地回答，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">这令我非常感动和感恩，觉得在我非常懵逼的时候有人拉了我一把。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">缺实习，赶紧去补。</strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">因为我申请是 BA、DS、MIS、CS 四个专业混申。 BA 专业很多是偏重于应用方面，虽然我已经在北大实验室有过两段科研，在 CMU 参加过暑研。但是这些并不能在应用领域增色，于是</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">&nbsp;Olive 老师建议我去补一段偏重应用的实习。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178); letter-spacing: 0px;"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178); letter-spacing: 0px;"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea95ce1ae50ef62882ff670" style="width: 308px; height: 445px;"/>&nbsp;<img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea95d10ae50ef62882ff677" style="width: 549px; height: 447px;"/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178); letter-spacing: 0px;">在实验室做的科研 demo “DeepCache”，</span><span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178); letter-spacing: 0px;">我们凭着这个成果到新德里参会</span>                    </p>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section>                                        <section>                                            <section>                                                <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                                    <span style="letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>                                                </p>                                                <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                                    <span style="letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></span>                                                </p>                                                <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                                    <span style="letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">这段实习是在西门子，是一个 data analysis 的工作，</span><span style="letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">有一次我们接了一个地铁的数据分析项目，客户有一个考验，要求我们先做一个小的 project ，我们就做了地铁门的故障率的预测，做出来跟客户汇报了之后，他们对结果非常满意，所以后来我们就签了一个更大的合同，分析地铁更多的运行情况。当时觉得很有成就感，很满足，听到客户说把数据分析的结果应用到地铁运行的过程中，</span><span style="letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">尝试用我们的方法达到节省能源和避免故障的作用，好像是自己为社会做出了一点点的贡献。</span><span style="letter-spacing: 1px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">这段经历也让我的文书多了一个很重要的亮点。</span>                                                </p>                                            </section>                                        </section>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">写 PS 没思路。</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">PS 毕竟有两面纸的空间，我根本不知道应该怎么去把它占满，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">每段都写什么？怎么引入？按什么顺序来说自己的经历？哪些要写哪些经历不写？怎么把经历跟具体的项目去有机地结合？最后怎么总结？</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">完全没什么思路。后来通过棕榈的素材挖掘器，通过它的提问，一步一步像采访的方式把思路捋清楚。而且雪峰老师也指导我，需要在 PS 里面体现什么特质，怎么跟经历具体结合，我们一起讨论，得出了一个提纲。</span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我中间有一段时期比较迷茫，因为实习、上课比较忙，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">处于一个比较沮丧的状态中，感觉压力很大，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">没有抽出时间来写 PS ，已经有挺长时间去卡在这个位置。当时 Olive 老师和雪峰老师就在群里和我聊天，问我情况怎么样，他们也觉得我最近的状态不是太好，需要做一些调整，所以当时对我激励挺大的，感觉有人一下点醒了我，这个事要放上日程，不然会错过一些 DDL 。我觉得很愧疚，毕竟这个事是我的事，我当时还不是特别上心，然后很快我就把 PS 做出来了，可以 move 到下一个事项。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在老师们的指导下，整个申请过程变得非常高效，有一些 DDL 是 3 月，但是我 1 月份就把所有的材料都交了。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);"><br/></span>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea95d54ae50ef62882ff684" style="width: 658px; height: 613px;"/>                    </p>                    <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="color: rgb(178, 178, 178); font-size: medium; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">（Olive 老师指导 PS 写作）</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(40, 167, 169); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">伯克利，意外之喜</strong>                    </p>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                    <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></strong>                                </p>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                    <p></p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">因为我比较早就拿到了 UC Davis 的 offer ，就像我前面说的我申的每个学校，即便只有这一个学校的录了我也会去，所以就有定心丸了。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我一直在等哥大的offer。我一开始没有太关注伯克利这个项目，但是这个 offer 比哥大的先来了一个礼拜，收到的时候开心得特别想大声笑，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">后来和导师对比了两个项目的就业前景、课程设置、培养方向，还是觉得这个伯克利的很适合我，算是意外之喜。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <br/>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">可能每个申请的朋友在准备的过程中都会遇到迷茫和困境，但是找到一些小小的技巧、敢于寻求帮助，我相信所有难题都会迎刃而解的。希望你们也能遇到申请路上的小惊喜、大收获。</span>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></strong>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">你想留学但是不知该如何申请？</span></strong>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">你觉得网申、写文书、找实习特难？</span></strong>                    </p>                    <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-hei