          type: '工科',
          content: '<h2 class="rich_media_title" id="activity-name" style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal;">    投实习全被拒，她为了翻盘一天只睡 2 小时，不服输最终带给她······</h2><div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list" style="margin: 0px 0px 22px; padding: 0px; line-height: 20px; font-size: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; position: relative; z-index: 1; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal;">    <br/></div><div id="js_album_area" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal;"></div><div class="rich_media_content " id="js_content" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: justify; position: relative; z-index: 0; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; visibility: visible;">    <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em;">        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1px;">她经历过</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">实习全被拒、备考 GRE 心态崩溃、GPA 低至 3.1</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1px;">，然而不服输的她凭借着要上名校的信念一路扛过所有艰辛<img class="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/b96CibCt70iaajvl7fD4ZCicMcjhXMp1v6UBxBaqVMicUHRNLhhIR0a8guFffxk6t4zJvJOOHDmnXQibRyPByKbiaCyA/640?tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; max-height: 20px !important; width: 20.3077px !important; visibility: visible !important;"/>，哪怕为了提高成绩</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">一天只能睡 2 个小时</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); letter-spacing: 1px;">，但拿到梦校 offer 那一刻，都值了<img class="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/b96CibCt70iaajvl7fD4ZCicMcjhXMp1v6UlVkLB96e4Ckndt2N6ghVR7vXD14pXwGjQBiaDBFI8kYgOUcYOWRYl6w/640?tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; max-height: 20px !important; width: 20px !important; visibility: visible !important;"/>。</span>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <p style="margin: 0px 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 1px;">棕榈&nbsp; L 学员</span></strong></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px;">&nbsp;▼</span></strong></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 20px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center;">                <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea95766ae50ef62882ff608" style="width: 220px; height: 217px;"/>            </p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: medium; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: left; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); caret-color: red; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;">本科：</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); caret-color: red; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-indent: 28px;">伦斯勒理工学院</span>&nbsp;机械工程</span><br/>            </p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: medium; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">GPA：</strong>3.49 / 4.0</span>            </p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: medium; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">GRE：</strong>323</span>            </p>            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 1em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: medium; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">Offer：</strong>康奈尔大学、杜克大学、哥伦比亚大学、约翰霍普金斯大学</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px; caret-color: red; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑;">、南加利福尼亚大学、圣路易斯华盛顿大学、伦斯勒理工学院</span>            </p>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section>                                        <hr style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"/>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>            <section>                <section></section>            </section>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="" style="margin: 0px 7px 11px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(20, 85, 87); border-top-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-right-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-left-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-radius: 3px; line-height: 36px; background: rgb(40, 167, 169);">受到打击后的翻盘</span></strong></span>                </section>            </section>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1px;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">大二<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">第一次参加招聘会的时候，我被深深的打击到了，</span>当时看到身边那些同学的简历觉得自己那点薄弱的经历完全拿不出手，挫败感特别强。除了经历丰富，那些同学的 GPA 也很高，大都在 3.5 以上，而一对比只有 3.3（最低到 3.1）的我真的太弱鸡了。而且当时<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我也试着去投了许多公司的实习岗位，结果一个 offer 都没拿到，</span>后来又有一些专业课的考试成绩也不如人意，这一连串的打击把我从大一时那种得过且过的状态中彻底打醒，开始重新重试学习这个事。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea95782ae50ef62882ff60c" style="width: 615px; height: 413px;"/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">后来几年，每到 final 的时候，熬夜已经成为常态，有时候<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">常常学习到 3、4 点，睡 2 个小时就起床继续复习然后去参加考试，</span>付出还是有收获的，之后我的 GPA 一直都是在往上升的，没有退步过。其实这种状态对于海本的同学来说可能都比较普遍，如果要说<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我最拼最拼的一段学习经历，那还是准备 GRE 的时候，那时真的是从早学到晚，基本没怎么休息，不停地学。</span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我清楚的记得第 2 次考 GRE 的时候<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我的心态非常差</span>，考试头一天心跳特别快，直到 3、4 点才睡着，第二天一早随便喝了 2 口粥就去考了，因为当时给自己定了 325 的目标，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">搞得整个人压力非常大</span>，最后考出来成绩只有 315，就比第一次裸考 314 只多了 1 分，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">当时看到这个成绩后非常崩溃，给我妈打电话边打边哭，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我就觉得为什么我这么拼地复习，这么努力却没有看到成效。</span></span>（后来才明白心态也是影响考试效果的关键）</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea95799ae50ef62882ff613" style="width: 624px; height: 416px;"/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">打完这通电话后我妈出于心疼我，就连忙帮我去咨询中介看看以当时 315 的 GRE 成绩和 GPA 大概能去到什么样档次的学校。当时我们同时咨询了好几家，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">对比下来后棕榈给我们的观感是最好的，因为态度很真诚。</span></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">有一些其他的中介在一开始就特别笃定地说冲刺常青藤没什么问题之类的，我和我妈听了都觉得挺不靠谱的（毕竟当时对自己的实力还是比较清楚），但在棕榈我们当时接触的那个学长，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">他就是一步步地分析我目前的一些背景条件，</span>比如他说<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我的 GPA 是一直呈上升趋势的，这样给招生官会留下比较好印象，</span>虽然总的 GPA 是 3.49，但专业 GPA 是 3.6，同时他也说道我有美本的优势，就算以目前的 GRE 成绩大概率也能申到一些不错的学校，不用太过焦虑。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea957b1ae50ef62882ff61a" style="width: 635px; height: 410px;"/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">整个沟通的过程都让我和我妈觉得很专业，说的话也是言之凿凿，所以<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">聊完之后我的心态也放松了很多，不像之前老是绷着一根弦，生怕考不到高的 GRE 就很多学校去不了。</span>而且后来棕榈的老师和我妈也一起开导我，给我信心，所以我第 3 次去考的时候整个人要轻松很多，最后 325 的成绩也证明对于考试来说心态有多么重要，要懂得适时给自己减压。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">当然最终会选择签约棕榈除了前面提到的沟通过程很愉快，还有一个非常重要的原因就是棕榈有实实在在可参考的申请案例。因为<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在我的上一届有一个学姐也是棕榈的学员，她是被斯坦福录取了的，当时让她帮忙介绍中介的时候她就极力推荐棕榈，</span>还有一些其他的学长学姐也是找棕榈录到了很多不错的学校，我和我妈都觉得<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">没有任何东西能比这种摆在自己面前活生生的案例来得更有说服力，</span>所以最后我们选择了棕榈，而现在我拿到的这些申请成果也证明了我们当初的选择没有错，棕榈带给我的不仅有我一直憧憬的常青藤（康奈尔、哥大）还有杜克、JHU 等名校，这些都是我之前不太敢奢望的。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea957c8ae50ef62882ff61e" style="width: 621px; height: 385px;"/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>            </p>            <section>                <section>                    <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span class="" style="margin: 0px 7px 11px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(20, 85, 87); border-top-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-right-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-left-color: rgb(20, 85, 87); border-radius: 3px; line-height: 36px; background: rgb(40, 167, 169);">通向名校的助力者们</span></strong></span>                </section>            </section>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">棕榈给我安排的专业导师是一名宾大的博士</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">，他带给我最大的感受就是提出的建议和教导的方法都非常有用，比如在写文书的过程中，因为我有好几段经历，看起来都是没什么联系的，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">但他总是有办法用很有逻辑的方式把它们串联起来，</span>显得顺理成章，思路脉络也很清晰。而且<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">有 2 段经历一开始我是觉得没什么好写的，后来他也给我挖了出来，</span>让我的文书丰富了许多。同时他也告诉我一定要写到自己是</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">如何克服困难做出了哪些成果的，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">他说这是招生官非常看重的东西。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">当然在整个文书修改的过程<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">他也给我加了很多机械工程的专业术语，因为他本身也是这个专业的，</span>所以这些对他而言比较驾轻就熟。我对我自己最后的申请文书成稿是非常满意的，既有个人特色又展示了专业能力。同时我觉得<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我跟专导比较合拍的一点是我们俩的步调特别一致，</span>我们都是那种不喜欢太赶也不喜欢太慢的，基本上<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">他每次让我返稿的 DDL 都让我觉得很合适，</span>所以申请的过程中我都不觉有多累，整个状态是很舒服的。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea957e9ae50ef62882ff624" style="width: 615px; height: 386px;"/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我的主导师饼姐是一个非常开朗乐观的人，她在我考 GRE 时为我解压不少，给了我很多信心。而且不管是<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">一开始选校为我提供许多表格、PDF 等干货信息，还是在文书后期润色时给我不断修改一些表达上的错误，增添一些文学性的东西等，</span>她在申请过程中一直都是操心操力的。包括后来需要面试，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">她除了给我许多面经，还帮我一道题一道题理思路，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">因为有时候我自己在回答比如为什么要选这所大学时往往一两句话就说完了，但饼姐说这是远远不够的，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">她会给我想一些更符合题目的点，列一些时间地点等其他讯息，以此展示我对周边情况比较了解，</span>这样在面试时也能说得比较专业，让人信服。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <br/>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">饼姐不仅跟我相处得很好，她跟我妈关系也很不错，我妈对她评价很高。因为有时候<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我妈不懂一些选校的内容或是她偶尔想了解一下我的近况等饼姐都会很耐心的跟我妈语音讲解，</span>用我妈的话来说就是她特别能理解家长的心情，也能在家长与孩子的关系调解上处理得很好，所以我妈也很喜欢她。</span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>            </p>            <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea95806ae50ef62882ff62e" style="width: 620px; height: 446px;"/></span>            </p>            <p style="margin: 0px 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;">                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !import