er-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); transform-origin: 0px 0px; transform: scale(1, 0.5); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: left; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); font-size: 14px;"></span>        </p>    </section>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section>                                        <section>                                            <section>                                                <section>                                                    <section>                                                        <section>                                                            <p style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                                                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">勇敢面对 “双非” 弱势</span></strong>                                                            </p>                                                            <section>                                                                <section>                                                                    <section>                                                                        <p class="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-width: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                                                            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">勇敢面对 “双非” 弱势</span></strong>                                                                        </p>                                                                    </section>                                                                </section>                                                            </section>                                                            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                                                <br/>                                                            </p>                                                        </section>                                                    </section>                                                </section>                                            </section>                                        </section>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <section>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">从高中开始，我对 Big Data 的概念就很感兴趣，“信息”、“计算”、“数据” 几个单词在脑海中铺陈开来，描绘着我未来继续前进的大概方向。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在高考发挥一般的情况下，虽然我没有去到自己心仪的学校，但所幸的是，我去到了喜欢的专业：信息管理，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">开始了向 Big Data 迈近的第一步，于是从大一开始，我就不断摸索自己合适的道路，并下决心在硕士阶段向计算机方向靠近。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">说起计算机、信息相关专业，我想很多人的第一选择都是美国，基于这个印象，我开始去了解美研的申请，于是</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">大一的时候就关注了各种留学机构的微信公众号、收听了几十场留学相关的讲座，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">多渠道搜集信息，在心理上做好了准备，对各大院校有了一个大概的轮廓和印象。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">在得知了美国留学申请在学生软实力、文书、标化等各个方面的严苛要求后，我意识到，在这个多维度综合考量学生能力的体系下，学校背景的权重并不具备压倒性，</span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">“双非” 虽然意味着竞争力的一定削弱，但是如果其他方面够出彩，或许可以弥补这个弱势</span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">——这也是美研一开始吸引我的地方：充满着不确定性和未知的挑战性，但机会对每个人来说相对公平，比起其他国家的 “语言标化” 一锤定音，更像是一场漫长而煎熬的持久战。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我个人认为，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在申请前期，不要对申请过程中的细节太纠结，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">比如哪些学校对学校背景有强烈的限制，文书应该怎么展开等等，仅仅停留在一个初步了解的阶段就足够了，一是为了减少时间成本，二是前两年是非常重要的蓄力阶段，需要一点幻想和憧憬来充值，心无旁骛地先把该做的都做了，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">有一点 “无知者无畏” 的意味，申请成功的可能性反而会更大。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;就拿我本人而言，“学校硬背景不够，软实力来凑”，这句充满了“蜜汁自信”的话可以说是支撑着我走过了漫长的申请之旅。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea95010ae50ef62882ff558" style="width: 613px; height: 421px;"/></span>        </p>    </section>    <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <strong style="font-size: 16px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">明确大致规划，及早准备</strong><br/>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <p class="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-width: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">明确大致规划，及早准备</strong></span>                            </p>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>                <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <br/>                </p>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <section>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我大学的前两年，主要处于一个向着目标不断打磨自己的阶段。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">专业课上，我一定是坐在前排的那个学生，用心对待每一次作业和测验，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">老师见过的学生数不胜数，可能过目就忘，但十足用心的肯定会给他们留下印象的。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我们专业的课程属于比较“万金油”的类型，JAVA 等硬核编程和管理学、经济学甚至是生产运营管理这种偏软的课程都会学，无论是否喜欢，我都抱着同样认真的态度来对待，因为越靠近申请季我就越坚信一个道理：</span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">GPA 和排名真的超级无敌霹雳重要，这个基础筹码一定要拿下，并且在能力范围内越高越好。</span></strong>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">有一次，学校组织了一堂类似专业导论的课程，讲课的教授非常优秀，研究方向也是我感兴趣的，在稳住了 GPA，拿到了国家奖学金之后，我鼓起勇气联系那位教授，希望能够加入她的课题组，最终如愿以偿。在这位教授的指导下，我参与了一项大创国家级项目、带领了一项省级项目，均提前一年结题，答辩评级均为“优秀”，在申请季的时候，也顺利获得了她的推荐信。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">这个故事是想告诉大家，如</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">果想要让喜欢的教授接纳你，不要拍拍脑袋没有任何准备就去打扰 ta，可以稍微对 ta 的研究方向有一定了解，或是在专业内达到一定的学习成绩排名，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">让 ta 自然而然地留意到你，后续会更容易有参与 ta 带领的课题的机会。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea9503bae50ef62882ff55e" style="width: 594px; height: 581px;"/></span>        </p>    </section>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <p class="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-width: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">做喜欢的事，在不同可能性中定义自己</span></strong>                            </p>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>                <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">做喜欢的事，在不同可能性中定义自己</span></strong>                </p>                <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                    <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><br/></span></strong>                </p>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <section>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">由于一早就定下了申请美帝研究生的目标，在课外，我通过各种渠道去留意是否有符合我的比赛机会，特别是对出国留学含金量较高的国际赛事。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">大一的时候，有一位哈佛教授来中国举办了一个</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">社会经济分析大赛，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">要求通过挖掘海量的县志数据并进行分析，最后输出全英文的报告。这个比赛非常符合我的预期，所以我参加了比赛，最后和团队一起获得了全国第 17 名的好成绩。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">大二的寒假，我和两位优秀的小伙伴一起</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">参加了美赛，血战三天三夜后获得了 M 奖。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">参与比赛对于我而言，拿奖固然重要，但参与过程中积累的技能树是更加宝贵的财富，因此比赛重质不重量，我更加倾向于专注在一件事情上，然后把它做到最好。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">大学的前两年所做的一切都是我感兴趣的，除了学术上的主线，过程中再不断加入一些新鲜的分支，比如利用自己的兴趣爱好去做一些大学才有机会做的事情：组建了一支乐队；参加各种各样的志愿活动，为智力缺陷的特殊人群提供陪伴、成为图书馆口语角的组织者、国际钢琴比赛赛务组的工作人员、去欧洲进行文化交流和探索等等；采访喜爱的 café 创始人，免费为她做社交网络推广；探索凌晨 5 点的学校，记录不为人知的豆浆店大叔、扫地阿姨的付出……</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <br/>        </p>    </section>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center; font-size: 17px;">                    <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea94c15ae50ef62882ff4e6" style="width: 601px; height: 330px;"/>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center;">                    <span style="color:#bfbfbf">（我的乐队）</span>                </p>                <p style="text-align: center;">                    <span style="color:#bfbfbf"><img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea95113ae50ef62882ff56a" style="width: 598px; height: 407px;"/></span>                </p>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <section>        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(178, 178, 178);">（<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px;">一起采访天使博物馆的创始人）</span></span>        </p>    </section>    <section></section>    <section>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>        </p>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <section>                        <section>                            <section>                                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; font-size: 80px; line-height: 1em; color: rgb(192, 200, 209);">“</span>&nbsp;                                <section></section>                            </section>                            <section>                                <section>                                    <section>                                        <section>                                            <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                                <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">音乐和摄影是我和外界沟通连接的桥梁，因为有它们的存在，我和有隔着将近二十年年龄鸿沟的家庭主妇、算命出版物作者、咖啡师、少年看守所的少年犯、手工艺者、大巴司机等各式各样的人建立了联系。它们不仅仅是我的爱好和兴趣，和 Volunteering 结合起来，更是成为了我与形形色色的人接触交流的契机，和我发现、感受世界的载体。我不仅可以通过他们抒发对生活的感受，还能对这个世界带来微不足道但确实存在的影响。&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>                                            </p>                                        </section>                                    </section>                                </section>                            </section>                            <section>                                <section></section><span style="margin: -0.11em 0px 0px -0.1em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; font-size: 80px; color: rgb(192, 200, 209);"><div style="text-align: right;">                                    <span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ”</span>                                </div></span>                            </section>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">——在提交给 CMU 的 Optional Essay 里我这样写道</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <br/>        </p>    </section>    <section>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">这篇 essay 很好地从不同于主材料的角度描绘了我作为理科生感性艺术的一面，以一个特殊的角度把爱好和生活串联了起来，丰富了我经历的维度。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">所以对于申请而言，所有的经历都可能是使申请文书立体化的有力的武器，建议大家可以在一个阶段过后就进行梳理和复盘，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">不至于在申请季的时候手忙脚乱，觉得素材不够。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"></span>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center;">            <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea95158ae50ef62882ff57d" style="width: 480px; height: 352px;"/>&nbsp;<img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea95171ae50ef62882ff58b" style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; width: 481px; height: 352px;"/>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span><br/>        </p>    </section>    <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <strong style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; background-color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><br/></span></strong>    </p>    <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <strong style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; background-color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><br/></span></strong>    </p>    <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <strong style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; background-color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><br/></span></strong>    </p>    <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <strong style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; background-color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">梦校 CMU 初了解</span></strong><br/>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p class="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-width: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">梦校 CMU 初了解</span></strong>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <br/>        </p>    </section>    <section>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我希望有人能指导我的申请，但是又想掌控申请进度和文书主动权，锻炼自己 multi-tasking 的能力，所以我对申请机构的半 DIY 模式很感兴趣。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">刚进大学的时候我就关注了棕榈的公众号，比起其他专注留学服务的中介，棕榈给我留下深刻印象的其实是它在各种学术分享的投入，我特别喜欢棕榈学院的每期干货课程，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">基本上线上讲座、分享会等每场我都会参与，有一种长期培养起来的熟悉感，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">于是我第一个拜访了棕榈的线下办公室，在这里遇到了 Jessie 。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">Jessie 真的非常有耐心，客观分析了我既定的背景，帮助我建立了合理的定位，详细介绍了申请季的各个流程和细节，也是这个机会让我了解到&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">CMU 的 MISM-Global 项目——不仅专排超前，可以在两个国家进行学习，有充分的时间为就业做准备，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">还可以选 CMU CS 学院的课程，最重要的是，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">这个项目前两年有软背景和我比较类似的录取案例。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">Jessie 给了我充足的信心，告诉我 CMU 并没有其他的学校那么看重申请者的学校背景，跳一跳，说不定可以够得到。也对比了其他一些机构，感觉都没有棕榈的印象好，于是自然地就选择了棕榈成为我申请路上的伙伴。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <br/>        </p>    </section>    <p style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">        <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(40, 167, 169); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">用心打磨文书，踏实积累</strong>    </p>    <section>        <section>            <section>                <section>                    <p class="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-width: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                        <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">用心打磨文书，踏实积累</strong></span>                    </p>                </section>            </section>        </section>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <br/>        </p>    </section>    <section>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">感觉自己在整个申请过程中最幸运的事情，就是遇到了一个超级 Nice 超级棒的团队，感恩之心不知道该从何说起。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">印象最深刻的，是前主导师 Ricky&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">从推荐信开始严格把关，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">一遍遍地帮助我</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">梳理 CV&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">的内容，身体抱恙还一直跟我耐心辅导；后来超级温柔认真负责（所有美好的形容词放在这里都不为过 TAT）的睿姐接手我之后，很快熟悉了我的特点和经历，和我一起</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">斟酌所有文书的一字一句，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">不嫌弃我严重的强迫症，我提出的每个点都和我一起修改到满意为止；还有来自 CMU 的非常专业的思思导师，非常耐心地</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">解答了我对 CMU 的一些问题，并给出了针对文书和面试的很多建议。</span>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea955e4ae50ef62882ff5d7" style="width: 628px; height: 620px;"/>        </p>    </section>    <section></section>    <section>        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(178, 178, 178);">（<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; letter-spacing: 0px;">和睿姐满满当当的聊天记录）</span></span>        </p>    </section>    <section>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <br/>        </p>    </section>    <section>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我印象特别深刻的是，写 PS 的时候我大部分的时间都被实习占用了，又因为严重的强迫症发作，导致定稿的时间非常短，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">我又因为没办法独自完成对素材进行筛选，一下子提交了几千字的初稿，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">是睿姐和思思导师在很短的时间内对我的初稿进行了修改，删去了没有那么重要的内容和元素，提炼出一篇</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">高度简洁明了又极具说服力的初稿。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">CMU 的 Optional Essay 也是经睿姐之手，才得以让我的各种想法的串联有了一个非常美好的落地（我实在是没有文笔 orz ），我还记得 CMU 的申请是第一个投递的，睿姐担心我第一个申请没有把关信息容易填错，一直陪我坚持到凌晨 3 点 (QAQ) ……睿姐真的刷新了我对中介的所有印象，真的很幸运能够遇到这么负责任的主导师。当然还有很棒的种子主导师 Sharon ，从 GT 考试和实习都给了我很详尽的建议和规划，甚至还给我提前进行了 CV 撰写培训；回复非常及时的高效的班主任 Elaine ，总是第一时间解答我对申请流程中的任何疑惑；当然还有从头到尾都万分负责的 Jessie ，一直是让我爸妈满意的存在。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span>        </p>       