 1em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); min-width: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">                                <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px;">GT 遭遇瓶颈，转战实习</span></strong>                            </p>                        </section>                    </section>                </section>            </section>        </section>    </section>    <section>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">以我自己而言，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">GT 两个考试仿佛总是跟我过不去，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">要不是单项发挥不稳定，总分上不去，要不就是投入了很长的时间学习，但得不到预期的效果，经历了很长的拉锯战，分数还是维持在 baseline ，一度心灰意冷。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">与此同时我没有停止简历的投递，在申请 DDL 前两个月拿到了 Tencent 的实习 Offer ，咨询了主导师睿姐的建议之后，下定决心去重新展开一段 Solid 的实习。实习重在质量和时间长短，有之前一段 6 个月的实习作铺垫，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">在鹅厂实习期间，我以公司的名义发明了专利，还拿到了转正的口头 offer ，相信这段经历在某个程度上，能够弥补标化方面的缺失。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">所以我想分享的是，当申请过程中遇到了死胡同，可以尝试拐个弯，丰富自己其他维度的经历。</span></strong>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <br/>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <img src="http://cms.palmdrive.cn/file/5ea9552aae50ef62882ff5c9" style="width: 535px; height: 564px;"/>        </p>        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            （腾讯实习）        </p>        <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <br/>        </p>    </section>    <section>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">我至今还记得，2 月最后一天接到第一个来自 CMU 的 dream offer 那个早晨，我看着邮箱里躺着的来自 “Heinz College” 的邮件，战战兢兢地打开，“Congratulations!” 映入眼帘，颤抖着看到了正式 offer ，还和睿姐确认了很多次是不是发错了。四年前的自己真的没有想过，自己能够越过重重障碍，最后得以梦想成真。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(40, 167, 169);">回头看看发现，这一路上遇到的无数困难，其实真的都不算什么。</span>        </p>        <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">            <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">&nbsp;</s